(35, 'Sajiero Women\'s Gown Set, Silk, Blue, Rivya', 'Clothing & Style', 'Women', '<h3><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Product Highlights:</span></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Material: Soft, smooth satin and luxurious silk.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Design: Floral lace at the sleeves for a delicate touch.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Fit: Free size, fits up to sizes 32, 36, 38, 40, 42, L, M, S, XL.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Care: Hand wash only.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Length: Long length for full coverage.</span></li></ol>', '<p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Rivya Silk Set Is A Smooth And Elegant Nightwear Combo Designed For Everyday Comfort. The Soft Silk Fabric Feels Gentle On The Skin, While The Lace Edges Add A Touch Of Style. The Set Includes A Knee Length Nighty And A Matching Long Robe, Perfect For Relaxing At Home Or For A Comfortable Night\'S Sleep.</span></p>', 2780, 2337, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-08 16:33:05', '[\"[\\\"M\\\",\\\"L\\\"]\"]'),
(36, 'Sajiero Women\'s 2-Piece Gown Set, Jersey Silk, Maroon', 'Clothing & Style', 'Women', '<h3><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Product Highlights:</span></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Two-Piece Set: Includes a shirt and a matching gown</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Material: Soft and breathable Jersey Silk</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Comfortable Fit: Designed for ease of movement</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Lightweight &amp; Flowing: Perfect for lounging or bedtime</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Stylish &amp; Versatile: Wear together or separately</span></li></ol>', '<p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Sajiero brings you this soft and comfortable Jersey Silk Gown Set, perfect for relaxing at home. This two-piece set includes a stylish shirt and a matching gown, designed for ease and elegance. The breathable jersey silk fabric feels smooth on the skin, making it an ideal choice for all seasons. Whether you\'re lounging or winding down for the night, this set offers both style and comfort.</span></p>', 3300, 2145, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-08 16:41:38', '[\"[\\\"S\\\",\\\"M\\\",\\\"L\\\"]\"]'),
(37, 'Printed Maxi For Women/Girl', 'Clothing & Style', 'Women', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Elegant Printed Design</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Soft &amp; Breathable Fabric</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Comfortable &amp; Flowing Fit</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight for Summer Wear</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Trendy &amp; Stylish Look</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Stitching</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Perfect for Casual &amp; Outings</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy to Maintain</strong></li></ol>', '<p>Step into effortless style and comfort with our Printed Maxi for Women and Girls. Designed for both casual outings and special occasions, this maxi dress features a vibrant, all-over print that adds a touch of elegance and playfulness to your wardrobe. Its flowing silhouette ensures a flattering fit for all body types, while the lightweight, breathable fabric keeps you cool and comfortable throughout the day. Perfect for summer gatherings, beach trips, or evening strolls, this maxi dress is your go-to choice for a chic, versatile look.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Eye-catching, vibrant printed design</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Flowy maxi length for a graceful silhouette</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Lightweight, breathable fabric for all-day comfort</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Suitable for casual, festive, or summer occasions</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Easy to style with sandals, heels, or flats</li></ol>', 4099, 3250, '[]', '[\"Blue\",\"Black\",\"Yellow\",\"Pink\"]', '2026-03-08 16:54:42', '[\"[\\\"S\\\",\\\"M\\\",\\\"L\\\"]\"]'),
(38, 'Zebra Lining Printed Maxi 2 Pcs', 'Clothing & Style', 'Women', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Zebra Printed Design</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Two-Piece Set</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Soft &amp; Breathable Fabric</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Comfortable &amp; Relaxed Fit</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight &amp; Summer-Friendly</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Stitching</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Trendy &amp; Stylish Look</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Perfect for Casual &amp; Outings</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy to Maintain</strong></li></ol>', '<p>Elevate your wardrobe with the Zebra Lining Printed Maxi 2-Piece Set, perfect for women and girls who love bold patterns with effortless style. This chic set features a striking zebra-inspired print, combining contemporary fashion with timeless elegance. The flowy maxi skirt ensures graceful movement, while the matching top completes the look with a coordinated, stylish appeal. Crafted from lightweight, breathable fabric, this set offers comfort without compromising on styleŌĆöideal for casual outings, summer parties, or festive occasions.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Trendy zebra lining print for a bold, fashionable statement</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>2-piece set: matching maxi skirt and top</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Flowing, comfortable maxi skirt with graceful movement</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Lightweight, breathable fabric for all-day comfort</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Versatile styling for casual, festive, or summer events</li></ol>', 4099, 3299, '[]', '[\"Blue\",\"Black\"]', '2026-03-08 17:01:05', '[\"[\\\"S\\\",\\\"M\\\",\\\"L\\\"]\"]');
