(48, 'Blake Adolf Shoes For Men', 'Footwear', 'Formal Shoes', '<h3><strong>Key Features ŌĆō MenŌĆÖs Formal Shoes</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium Leather Material</strong> ŌĆō Made from high-quality cow leather for durability and elegance.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Classic Loafer / Oxford Style</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for office, formal events, and business meetings.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Comfortable Insole</strong> ŌĆō Cushioned interior for all-day comfort.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Rubber Sole</strong> ŌĆō Slip-resistant sole for secure walking.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Polished Finish</strong> ŌĆō Elegant look suitable for professional attire.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight &amp; Flexible</strong> ŌĆō Easy to wear without compromising on support.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Breathable Lining</strong> ŌĆō Helps keep feet fresh throughout the day</li></ol>', '<p>Step into sophistication with these <strong>premium leather formal shoes</strong> designed for the modern man. Crafted from <strong>high-quality cow leather</strong>, these shoes offer a <strong>polished and elegant finish</strong>, perfect for office wear, business meetings, or formal occasions.</p><p>The <strong>cushioned insole</strong> ensures all-day comfort, while the <strong>durable rubber sole</strong> provides excellent grip and stability. With <strong>breathable lining</strong> and <strong>lightweight construction</strong>, these shoes combine style and comfort effortlessly.</p><p>Available in <strong>multiple size