(50, 'Men\'s Formal Shoes US-BY-5305', 'Footwear', 'Formal Shoes', '<h3><strong>Key Features</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium Quality Material</strong> ŌĆō Crafted with high-quality leather for a stylish and durable finish.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Rubber Outsole</strong> ŌĆō Strong and slip-resistant sole for better grip and stability.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight Construction</strong> ŌĆō Designed to provide ease and comfort while walking.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Breathable Inner Lining</strong> ŌĆō Helps keep feet fresh and comfortable throughout the day.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Smart &amp; Versatile Look</strong> ŌĆō Pairs perfectly with suits, dress pants, and formal outfits.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Perfect for Daily Formal Wear</strong> ŌĆō Ideal for office, weddings, and special occasions.</li></ol>', '<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">Designed with precision and crafted from </span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">cow full-grain leather</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">, this style delivers durability, sophistication, and everyday comfort. The </span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">synthetic lining</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\"> ensures a soft interior feel, while the </span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">padded in-sock</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\"> cushions every step. A </span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">TPR outsole</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\"> adds flexibility and reliable grip, making it perfect for both work and casual wear.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">Where </span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">refined craftsmanship</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\"> meets </span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">modern functionality</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\"> ŌĆö built to look sharp and feel effortless all day.</span></p><p><br></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(35, 35, 35);\">Signature Craftsmanship</strong></h3><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">Cow Full-Grain Leather Upper</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\"> ŌĆō premium finish with natural strength</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">Soft Synthetic Lining</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\"> ŌĆō smooth and comfortable interior</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">Padded In-Sock</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\"> ŌĆō enhanced cushioning for daily wear</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\">TPR Outsole</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(60, 60, 60);\"> ŌĆō durable, flexible, and slip-resistant</s