(52, 'GR-42 BLACK For Men', 'Footwear', 'Formal Shoes', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Premium black finish</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Classic formal design</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Comfortable cushioned insole</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Durable rubber sole</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Lightweight and flexible</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Breathable inner lining</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ideal for office and formal wear</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Stylish and versatile look</li></ol>', '<p>Upgrade your wardrobe with the <strong>GR-42 Black For Men</strong>, designed for men who value both style and comfort. Crafted with a sleek black finish, these shoes offer a timeless formal look that pairs perfectly with office wear, business suits, or special occasions. The premium construction ensures durability while maintaining a sophisticated appearance.</p><p><br></p><p>The soft inner lining and comfortable fit allow you to wear them for long hours without discomfort. Its sturdy sole provides excellent grip and stability, making it ideal for daily use. Whether you\'re heading to work, a meeting, or a formal event, the GR-42 Black shoes deliver confidence and elegance with every step.</p>', 9499, 7699, '[\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 8\"]', '[]', '2026-03-09 06:46:40', '[\"[]\"]'),
(53, 'LEATHER SHOES - RPD-02 GREEN', 'Footwear', 'Formal Shoes', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Premium green leather finish</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Elegant formal design</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Cushioned comfort insole</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Durable slip-resistant sole</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Lightweight and flexible</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Breathable lining for all-day wear</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Perfect for office and formal occasions</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Stylish and versatile look</li></ol>', '<p>Step up your footwear game with the <strong>RPD-02 Green Leather Shoes</strong>, crafted for men who appreciate style, quality, and comfort. Made from genuine leather, these shoes boast a rich green hue that adds a unique touch to your formal or semi-formal outfits.</p><p>Designed for all-day wear, the soft inner lining and cushioned insole ensure comfort without compromising on elegance. The sturdy rubber sole provides excellent traction and durability, making them perfect for both office use and special occasions. Stand out with a blend of sophistication and modern design.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Highlights:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Stylish green leather design for a distinctive look</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Soft and comfortable inner lining for long hours of wear</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"fa