(54, 'LEATHER SHOES - NCF-20 TAN', 'Footwear', 'Formal Shoes', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Premium tan leather finish</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Classic formal design</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Cushioned insole for comfort</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Durable slip-resistant sole</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Lightweight and flexible</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Breathable inner lining</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Perfect for office and formal wear</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Stylish and versatile appearance</li></ol>', '<p>Elevate your formal footwear collection with the <strong>NCF-20 Tan Leather Shoes</strong>, crafted for men who value timeless style and lasting comfort. Made from premium genuine leather, the warm tan color adds a refined touch to both office wear and special occasion outfits.</p><p><br></p><p>The soft inner lining and cushioned footbed ensure all-day comfort, while the durable sole provides reliable traction and stability. Perfect for everyday wear or formal events, the NCF-20 Tan Leather Shoes combine sophistication with practicality.</p>', 12650, 9499, '[\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 8\",\"US/PAK 7\"]', '[]', '2026-03-09 07:42:36', '[\"[]\"]'),
