(57, 'Clutch Handbags For Women', 'Bags & Accessories', 'Handbags', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Elegant and compact design</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Premium quality material for durability</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Lightweight and easy to carry</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Secure zipper or magnetic closure</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Perfect for parties, events, and casual outings</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Stylish accessory to complement any outfit</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Multiple compartments for essentials</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Sleek and versatile look</li></ol>', '<p>Make a stylish statement with <strong>Clutch Handbags For Women</strong>, the perfect accessory for evenings, parties, or special occasions. Designed to combine elegance with convenience, these clutches offer a sleek, compact design without compromising on functionality.</p><p><br></p><p>Elevate your accessory game with the<strong> Clutch Handbags For Women</strong>, designed for women who love combining style, elegance, and convenience. These clutches are perfect for parties, evening events, weddings, or any special occasion where you want to make a lasting impression. Crafted with attention to detail, each clutch features high-quality materials that ensure durability while maintaining a polished and luxurious look.</p><p><br></p><p>With a variety of colors, textures, and designs to choose from, these clutches effortlessly complement any outfit ŌĆö from sleek evening dresses to contemporary formal wear. The<strong> Clutch Handbags For Women</strong> are more than just an accessory; they are a statement of sophistication, confidence, and timeless style for the modern woman who values both fashion and practicality.</p>', 2500, 2150, '[]', '[\"Red\",\"Black\",\"Brown\",\"Blue\"]', '2026-03-09 08:02:14', '[\"[]\"]'),
(58, 'Hand Bag 3Pcs', 'Bags & Accessories', 'Handbags', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Set of 3 stylish handbags in matching design</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Premium quality material for durability</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Spacious compartments for essentials</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Lightweight and easy to carry</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Secure zipper or magnetic closures</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Versatile for office, casual, and daily use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Elegant and fashionable accessory</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Perfect gift option for women</li></ol>', '<p>Upgrade your accessory collection with the <strong>Hand Bag 3Pcs Set</strong>, thoughtfully designed for women who love style, organization, and versatility. This set includes three handbags of varying sizes, perfect for different occasions ŌĆö from casual outings and office use to evening events and travel.</p><p>Crafted from high-quality materials, each bag offers durability while maintaining a chic and fashionable look. The spacious interiors and multiple compartments help you keep essentials like your wallet, phone, keys, makeup, and other personal items neatly organized. Lightweight and easy to carry, these bags provide both practicality and elegance, allowing you to switch effortlessly between bags depending on your needs.</p><p>Whether paired together or used separately, the <strong>Hand Bag 3Pcs Set</strong> adds a touch of sophistication to any outfit, making it a must-have for the modern woman who values both fashion and functionality.</p>', 3999, 2999, '[]', '[\"Black\",\"Brown\",\"Pink\"]', '2026-03-09 08:07:01', '[\"[]\"]'),
(59, 'Rangoon Messenger Bag For Women', 'Bags & Accessories', 'Handbags', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Stylish and modern messenger bag design</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Made with premium quality material for durability</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Spacious main compartment with multiple pockets</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Comfortable adjustable shoulder strap</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Secure zipper or magnetic closure</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Lightweight and easy to carry</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Perfect for office, college, or casual outings</li></ol>', '<p>Step into effortless style with the <strong>Rangoon Messenger Bag For Women</strong>, designed for women who value both fashion and practicality. Perfect for daily use, work, or casual outings, this messenger bag combines a sleek, modern design with versatile functionality.</p><p>Crafted from high-quality materials, it offers durability and a refined look that complements any outfit. The spacious main compartment and multiple pockets provide organized storage for essentials like your phone, wallet, keys, makeup, and even small notebooks or tablets. The adjustable strap ensures comfortable carrying, whether worn across the body or over the shoulder.</p><p>Lightweight yet sturdy, the <strong>Rangoon Messenger Bag</strong> is ideal for busy lifestyles without compromising on style. Its timeless design, practicality, and elegant finish make it a must-have accessory for the modern woman who wants to stay organized while looking effortlessly chic.</p>', 3000, 2500, '[]', '[\"Black\",\"Brown\"]', '2026-03-09 08:14:19', '[\"[]\"]'),
(60, 'ZamZam Floral Beauty Printed Tote Bag', 'Bags & Accessories', 'Handbags', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Elegant floral print design for a stylish look</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Made with high-quality durable material</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Spacious interior to carry essentials</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Lightweight and easy to carry</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Comfortable handles for shoulder or hand use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Secure zipper or open-top closure</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Perfect for casual outings, shopping, or daily use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Trendy and versatile accessory for women</li></ol>', '<p>Add a touch of elegance and charm to your everyday look with the <strong>ZamZam Floral Beauty Printed Tote Bag</strong>. Featuring a vibrant floral design, this tote bag is perfect for women who love combining style with practicality. Ideal for casual outings, shopping trips, or beach days, it brings a fresh, lively aesthetic to any outfit.</p><p>Made from high-quality materials, the bag is durable yet lightweight, making it easy to carry throughout the day. Its spacious interior comfortably holds essentials like your wallet, phone, keys, makeup, books, and more. The sturdy handles and reinforced stitching ensure reliable use, while the eye-catching floral print makes it a standout accessory.</p><p>Whether for daily errands, travel, or leisure activities, the <strong>ZamZam Floral Beauty Printed Tote Bag</strong> is a versatile and fashionable choice for women who want to combine functionality with timeless style.</p>', 780, 650, '[]', '[\"Red\",\"White\",\"Brown\",\"Blue\"]', '2026-03-09 08:20:09', '[\"[]\"]'),
(61, 'Rangoon Double Handle Tote Bag For Women', 'Bags & Accessories', 'Handbags', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Stylish double-handle design for easy carrying</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Made with premium quality durable material</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Spacious interior with multiple compartments</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Lightweight and comfortable to carry</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Secure zipper or magnetic closure</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Perfect for office, shopping, or casual outings</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Elegant and versatile accessory for everyday use</li></ol>', '<p>Enhance your everyday style with the <strong>Rangoon Double Handle Tote Bag For Women</strong>, designed to combine elegance with functionality. Perfect for work, shopping, travel, or casual outings, this tote bag offers a versatile and chic accessory that complements any outfit.</p><p>Crafted from high-quality materials, it ensures durability while maintaining a polished look. The spacious interior provides ample room for essentials like your wallet, phone, keys, makeup, and even small notebooks or tablets. Thoughtfully designed compartments help keep everything organized and easily accessible. The double handles offer comfortable carrying, whether over the shoulder or by hand.</p><p>Lightweight yet sturdy, the <strong>Rangoon Double Handle Tote Bag</strong> is ideal for women who value both style and practicality. With its timeless design and functional features, itŌĆÖs a must-have accessory that blends fashion with everyday convenience.</p>', 4500, 3700, '[]', '[\"Yellow\",\"Green\",\"Blue\",\"Brown\"]', '2026-03-09 08:25:05', '[\"[]\"]');
INSERT INTO `products` (`_id`, `name`, `category`, `subCategory`, `about`, `description`, `price`, `offerPrice`, `footwear_sizes`, `colors`, `created_at`, `sizes`) VALUES
(62, 'HM Hair Shampoo 150ml', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Shampoo & Facewashes', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Enriched formula for healthy and strong hair</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Gently cleanses scalp and hair</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Suitable for all hair types</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Adds shine and softness to hair</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Mild and safe for daily use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Refreshing fragrance for a pleasant experience</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Helps reduce hair damage and split ends</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Compact 150ml bottle, perfect for home or travel</li></ol>', '<p>Refresh and rejuvenate your hair with <strong>HM Hair Shampoo 150ml</strong>, a specially formulated hair care essential designed to cleanse deeply while maintaining natural moisture. Perfect for everyday use, this shampoo gently removes dirt, oil, and buildup without stripping your hair of its essential nutrients.</p><p>Enriched with quality ingredients that help support scalp health, HM Hair Shampoo leaves your hair feeling soft, smooth, and revitalized from root to tip. The balanced formula helps reduce frizz, enhance shine, and improve manageability, making your hair look and feel its best with every wash.</p><p>Ideal for all hair types, this 150ml bottle is compact and travelŌĆæfriendly, so you can keep your hair care routine on point wherever you go. Make <strong>HM Hair Shampoo 150ml</strong> a staple in your grooming lineup for consistently clean, healthyŌĆælooking hair</p>', 900, 750, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 08:59:29', '[\"[]\"]'),
(63, 'Marham Herbal Anti Hairfall Miracle Shampoo', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Shampoo & Facewashes', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Herbal formula to reduce hair fall naturally</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Strengthens hair from root to tip</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Gently cleanses scalp and hair</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Adds shine, softness, and volume</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Suitable for all hair types</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Free from harsh chemicals</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Promotes healthy hair growth</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Refreshing fragrance for a pleasant experience</li></ol>', '<p>Experience the power of nature with <strong>Marham Herbal Anti Hairfall Miracle Shampoo</strong>, expertly formulated to target hair fall while nourishing your scalp and strands. Infused with herbal extracts, this shampoo helps cleanse deeply without stripping away essential oils, promoting a healthier scalp environment that supports stronger, fuller hair.</p><p>Each wash works to reduce breakage and strengthen hair from root to tip, helping minimize hair fall caused by daily styling, pollution, and stress. The gentle, sulfateŌĆæfree formula leaves your hair feeling soft, refreshed, and more manageable, with improved texture and shine.</p><p>Perfect for those seeking a natural solution to hair fall concerns, <strong>Marham Herbal Anti Hairfall Miracle Shampoo</strong> brings together therapeutic herbs and modern care to help restore confidence in your hairŌĆÖs strength and vitality. Incorporate it into your hair care routine for visibly healthier, resilient hair with every wash.</p>', 2500, 2000, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 09:05:12', '[\"[]\"]'),
(64, 'Wellice Onion Anti Hair Loss Shampoo', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Shampoo & Facewashes', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Infused with onion extract to help reduce hair fall</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Strengthens hair roots and promotes healthier growth</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Gently cleanses scalp and hair</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Helps improve scalp circulation</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Adds shine and softness to hair</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Suitable for all hair types</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Free from harsh chemicals like sulfates &amp; parabens</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Refreshing fragrance for a pleasant wash experience</li></ol>', '<p>Give your hair the care it deserves with <strong>Wellice Onion Anti Hair Loss Shampoo</strong>, a powerful formula designed to combat hair loss while nourishing your scalp and strands. Enriched with onion extract and other beneficial ingredients, this shampoo helps stimulate the scalp, promote healthier hair growth, and reduce thinning and breakage.</p><p>The gentle yet effective cleansing action removes dirt, excess oil, and buildup without stripping your hairŌĆÖs natural moisture. Regular use leaves your hair feeling stronger, smoother, and more resilient, while the enriched nutrients help improve hair texture and shine. Ideal for all hair types, this shampoo is perfect for anyone seeking a naturalŌĆæinspired solution to hair fall concerns.</p><p>Make <strong>Wellice Onion Anti Hair Loss Shampoo</strong> part of your daily hair care routine for visibly healthier, more manageable hair with renewed strength and vitality.</p>', 1199, 999, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 09:16:39', '[\"[]\"]'),
(65, 'Shop Zone Lichen Black Hair Color Shampoo 200ml', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Shampoo & Facewashes', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>DualŌĆæaction shampoo with hair coloring and cleansing</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Rich black shade for natural, longŌĆælasting color</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Gentle formula that nourishes hair while coloring</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Helps cover grey hair effectively</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Enriched with conditioners for smooth, shiny hair</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Suitable for all hair types</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Easy to use and rinse</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Convenient 200ml size for regular use or travel</li></ol>', '<p>Refresh your look with the <strong>Shop Zone Lichen Black Hair Color Shampoo 200ml</strong>, a unique shampoo that not only cleanses your hair but also gradually enhances your natural black color with every wash. Perfect for those who want rich, vibrant black hair without the mess of traditional dyes, this shampoo combines gentle cleansing with subtle, longŌĆælasting color enhancement.</p><p>Formulated to nourish your hair while depositing natural black pigment, it helps improve shine and depth of color, leaving your hair looking healthier and more vibrant. The 200ml size is ideal for regular use and fits conveniently into your daily hair care routine.</p><p>Whether youŌĆÖre covering early greys or simply boosting your natural shade, <strong>Shop Zone Lichen Black Hair Color Shampoo 200ml</strong> delivers color and care together ŌĆö giving you beautifully black, shiny, manageable hair with every wash.</p>', 1699, 1399, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 09:20:34', '[\"[]\"]'),
(66, 'Invoke Skin Health Floral Anti Acne Facewash 50ml', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Shampoo & Facewashes', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>FloralŌĆæinfused formula that refreshes and cleanses</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Helps fight acne and blemishes</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Gently removes dirt, oil &amp; impurities</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Suitable for daily use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>AlcoholŌĆæfree and mild on skin</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Helps unclog pores and prevent breakouts</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Leaves skin soft, smooth &amp; refreshed</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Compact 50ml size ŌĆö perfect for home or travel</li></ol>', '<p>Refresh and purify your skin with <strong>Invoke Skin Health Floral AntiŌĆæAcne Facewash 50ml</strong>, specially formulated to target acne and breakouts while being gentle on your skin. Enriched with floral extracts and skinŌĆæloving ingredients, this facewash helps remove excess oil, dirt, and impurities that can clog pores and lead to acne.</p><p>The soothing formula works to calm inflammation and reduce redness, promoting a clearer, smoother complexion without overŌĆædrying. Its lightweight texture lathers softly, leaving your skin feeling clean, refreshed, and balanced after every wash.</p><p>Compact and travelŌĆæfriendly, the 50ml size makes it perfect for daily use at home or on the go. Make <strong>Invoke Skin Health Floral AntiŌĆæAcne Facewash 50ml</strong> a part of your skincare routine for healthierŌĆælooking skin with improved clarity and comfort.</p>', 700, 650, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 09:30:39', '[\"[]\"]'),
(67, 'Organic Bloom Activated Charcoal Facewash - 100ml', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Shampoo & Facewashes', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Activated Charcoal Formula</strong> ŌĆō Deep cleanses by drawing out dirt and impurities</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Organic Ingredients</strong> ŌĆō Gentle and safe for regular use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Unclogs Pores</strong> ŌĆō Helps absorb excess oil and reduces breakouts</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Refreshing &amp; Purifying</strong> ŌĆō Leaves skin feeling clean and revitalized</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Suitable for All Skin Types</strong> ŌĆō Especially effective for oily or acneŌĆæprone skin</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Mild &amp; NonŌĆæIrritating</strong> ŌĆō Free from harsh chemicals</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>100ml TravelŌĆæFriendly Size</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for home and onŌĆætheŌĆægo use</li></ol>', '<p>Revitalize your skincare routine with <strong>Organic Bloom Activated Charcoal Facewash ŌĆō 100ml</strong>, a powerful yet gentle cleanser designed to draw out impurities and refresh your complexion. Enriched with activated charcoal, this facewash works deep within pores to remove dirt, excess oil, and environmental pollutants that can dull your skin.</p><p>The rich, purifying formula helps unclog blocked pores and reduce the appearance of blackheads, leaving your skin feeling clean, smooth, and rejuvenated. Its naturalŌĆæinspired ingredients make it suitable for all skin types, especially oily and combination skin that needs extra clarity without harsh stripping.</p><p>Lightweight and easy to use, the 100ml size is perfect for daily cleansing at home or while traveling. Bring balance and brightness back to your skin with <strong>Organic Bloom Activated Charcoal Facewash ŌĆō 100ml</strong> for a fresher, healthierŌĆælooking complexion every day.</p>', 850, 750, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 09:34:05', '[\"[]\"]'),
(68, 'Organic Bloom Anti Acne Facewash - 100ml', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Shampoo & Facewashes', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Powerful AntiŌĆæAcne Formula</strong> ŌĆō Helps fight acne and breakouts</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Gentle &amp; Organic Ingredients</strong> ŌĆō Safe for daily use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Deep Cleansing Action</strong> ŌĆō Removes dirt, oil, and impurities</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Unclogs Pores</strong> ŌĆō Helps reduce blackheads and blemishes</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Hydrating &amp; NonŌĆæDrying</strong> ŌĆō Leaves skin soft and refreshed</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Suitable for All Skin Types</strong> ŌĆō Especially good for oily/acneŌĆæprone skin</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Mild &amp; NonŌĆæIrritating</strong> ŌĆō Free from harsh chemicals</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>TravelŌĆæFriendly 100ml Size</strong> ŌĆō Easy to carry</li></ol>', '<p>Refresh your skincare routine with <strong>Organic Bloom Anti Acne Facewash ŌĆō 100ml</strong>, thoughtfully formulated to help fight acne and promote a clearer complexion. Infused with naturalŌĆæinspired ingredients, this facewash works gently yet effectively to remove dirt, excess oil, and impurities that can clog pores and lead to breakouts.</p><p>Its soothing formula helps calm inflammation and reduce redness while cleansing deep into the skin, leaving your face feeling clean, balanced, and refreshed without overŌĆædrying. Suitable for daily use, this facewash supports healthierŌĆælooking skin with continued use, making it ideal for those dealing with acneŌĆæprone or troubled skin.</p><p>The convenient 100ml size is perfect for everyday skincare routines at home or on the go. Make <strong>Organic Bloom Anti Acne Facewash ŌĆō 100ml</strong> a part of your routine for clearer, calmer, and more radiant skin every day.</p>', 1099, 850, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 09:38:18', '[\"[]\"]'),
(69, 'Thermaltake UX400 ARGB Sync CPU Cooler', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Mobile & Computers', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>ARGB Sync Lighting</strong> ŌĆō 9 addressable LEDs with 16.8M color effects. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>High Cooling Performance</strong> ŌĆō Supports up to <strong>240W TDP</strong> for efficient CPU cooling. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>120mm High-Airflow Fan</strong> ŌĆō Provides strong airflow up to <strong>62.72 CFM</strong>. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Four Copper Heat Pipes</strong> ŌĆō Direct-contact heat pipes for fast heat transfer. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Quiet Operation</strong> ŌĆō Low noise level around <strong>25 dBA</strong> for silent performance. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Hydraulic Bearing Fan</strong> ŌĆō Improves durability and reduces friction. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Universal CPU Compatibility</strong> ŌĆō Supports Intel (LGA 1700/1200/115x) and AMD (AM5/AM4). </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Motherboard RGB Sync Support</strong> ŌĆō Works with ASUS Aura Sync, MSI Mystic Light, Gigabyte RGB Fusion, and ASRock Polychrome.</li></ol>', '<p><strong>Thermaltake UX400 ARGB Sync CPU Cooler Black ŌĆō High-Performance Cooling with Stunning RGB Lighting</strong></p><p>Upgrade your PC cooling system with the <strong>Thermaltake UX400 ARGB Sync CPU Cooler Black</strong>, designed to deliver powerful air cooling while enhancing the look of your gaming or workstation setup. Built with a sleek black heatsink and vibrant addressable RGB lighting, this cooler combines performance and style for modern PC builds.</p><p>The cooler features <strong>four 6mm copper heat pipes</strong> that make direct contact with the CPU, ensuring fast and efficient heat transfer. Paired with a <strong>120mm high-airflow fan</strong>, it provides excellent cooling performance to keep your processor running smoothly during gaming, multitasking, or heavy workloads. </p><p>The ARGB fan includes multiple addressable LEDs that support up to <strong>16.8 million colors</strong>, allowing you to synchronize lighting effects with popular motherboard RGB software such as ASUS Aura Sync, MSI Mystic Light, Gigabyte RGB Fusion, and ASRock Polychrome.</p>', 8450, 6670, '[]', '[\"Black\",\"White\"]', '2026-03-09 10:14:29', '[\"[]\"]'),
(70, 'Thermaltake Toughpower PT 1200W Power Supply', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Mobile & Computers', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>1200W High Power Output</strong> ŌĆō Provides stable 1200W continuous power for high-performance PCs. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>80 PLUS Platinum Efficiency</strong> ŌĆō Up to <strong>92% efficiency</strong>, reducing power loss and heat. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>ATX 3.1 &amp; PCIe 5.1 Ready</strong> ŌĆō Supports next-generation GPUs with native <strong>12+4 pin (12V-2x6) connectors</strong>. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Fully Modular Design</strong> ŌĆō Modular cables for easier installation and cleaner cable management. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>100% Japanese Capacitors</strong> ŌĆō Ensures long-term durability and reliable power delivery. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>135mm Hydraulic Bearing Fan</strong> ŌĆō Quiet cooling with efficient airflow. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Strong Single +12V Rail</strong> ŌĆō Provides stable and consistent power for demanding components. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Advanced Protection Features</strong> ŌĆō Includes OCP, OVP, UVP, OPP, SCP, and OTP for system safety.</li></ol>', '<p><strong>Thermaltake Toughpower PT 1200W Power Supply ŌĆō Platinum Efficiency &amp; Extreme Performance</strong></p><p>Power your high-end PC with the <strong>Thermaltake Toughpower PT 1200W Power Supply</strong>, engineered for demanding gaming systems, workstations, and content-creation builds. Delivering a massive <strong>1200W of continuous power</strong>, this premium PSU ensures stable and reliable performance even during heavy workloads or intense gaming sessions. </p><p>Built with <strong>80 PLUS Platinum certification</strong>, the power supply achieves up to <strong>92% efficiency</strong>, helping reduce heat, minimize energy loss, and keep your system running efficiently. This makes it an excellent choice for power-hungry CPUs and GPUs while maintaining optimal energy usage. </p><p>The Toughpower PT 1200W features <strong>100% high-quality Japanese 105┬░C capacitors</strong> for long-term durability and consistent power delivery. Its advanced <strong>LLC + DC-to-DC circuit design</strong> ensures precise voltage regulation and a strong single +12V rail for reliable performance under heavy loads. </p><p>To keep your system cool and quiet, the PSU includes a <strong>135mm hydraulic/FDB cooling fan</strong> that provides efficient airflow while maintaining low noise levels. The <strong>fully modular cable design</strong> allows clean cable management and improved airflow inside the case, giving your PC a neat and professional build.</p>', 22420, 18970, '[]', '[\"Grey\"]', '2026-03-09 10:20:01', '[\"[]\"]'),
(71, 'Thermaltake The Tower 600 Mid Tower Chassis', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Mobile & Computers', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Unique Vertical Case Design</strong> ŌĆō Stylish octagonal prism shape for a distinctive PC build. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Tempered Glass Panels</strong> ŌĆō Three 3 mm glass panels for a clear view of internal components. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>High Cooling Support</strong> ŌĆō Supports up to <strong>13├Ś120 mm fans or 9├Ś140 mm fans</strong> for powerful airflow. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Large Radiator Compatibility</strong> ŌĆō Supports up to <strong>420 mm radiator (right)</strong> and <strong>360 mm radiator (left)</strong>. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Wide Motherboard Support</strong> ŌĆō Compatible with <strong>Mini-ITX, Micro-ATX, and ATX</strong> motherboards. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Rotatable PCI-E Slots</strong> ŌĆō Allows flexible GPU installation options. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Modern Front I/O Ports</strong> ŌĆō Includes <strong>USB-C, USB 3.0 ports, and HD audio</strong>.</li></ol>', '<p>The Thermaltake The Tower 600 Mid Tower Chassis is a premium PC case designed for gamers, enthusiasts, and creators who want powerful performance with a unique visual style. Featuring a distinctive <strong>vertical octagonal design with tempered glass panels</strong>, this chassis offers a stunning showcase for high-end components while maintaining excellent airflow and cooling efficiency. </p><p>Built for modern PC builds, the case supports <strong>Mini-ITX, Micro-ATX, and ATX motherboards</strong>, giving builders flexibility for a wide range of configurations. Its spacious interior allows installation of large hardware components, including GPUs up to <strong>400 mm in length</strong>, CPU coolers up to <strong>210 mm</strong>, and power supplies up to <strong>220 mm</strong>, making it ideal for high-performance gaming systems and workstations. </p><p>Cooling performance is one of the key highlights of the Tower 600. The chassis supports <strong>up to thirteen 120 mm fans or nine 140 mm fans</strong>, along with <strong>420 mm radiators on the right side and 360 mm radiators on the left side</strong>, providing powerful airflow for demanding setups. Two 140 mm fans are pre-installed on the top to enhance thermal efficiency.</p>', 49790, 45770, '[]', '[\"White\",\"Black\"]', '2026-03-09 10:28:03', '[\"[]\"]'),
(72, 'Vento VG15FE 4x RGB Fans ATX Mid Tower and Vento 550W Power Supply', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Mobile & Computers', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>ATX Mid-Tower Gaming Case</strong> ŌĆō Compatible with ATX, Micro-ATX, and Mini-ITX motherboards. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>4 Pre-Installed RGB Fans</strong> ŌĆō 3├Ś120 mm front fans and 1├Ś120 mm rear fan for strong airflow and RGB lighting. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Mesh Front Panel Design</strong> ŌĆō Provides improved airflow for better system cooling. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Tempered Glass Side Panel</strong> ŌĆō Displays internal components and RGB lighting clearly. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>550W Power Supply Included</strong> ŌĆō Reliable power for gaming and everyday PC builds. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Support for Up to 6 Fans</strong> ŌĆō Additional fan mounts available for enhanced cooling. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Convenient Front I/O Ports</strong> ŌĆō Includes 1├ŚUSB 3.0, 2├ŚUSB 2.0, and HD audio ports. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Spacious Interior Design</strong> ŌĆō Supports GPUs up to ~340 mm and CPU coolers up to ~160ŌĆō165 mm height.</li></ol>', '<p>Upgrade your PC setup with the <strong>Vento VG15FE 4x RGB Fans ATX Mid Tower</strong>, paired with a <strong>Vento 550W Power Supply</strong>, designed for gamers and PC enthusiasts who want both performance and visual style. This gaming chassis features a modern design with vibrant RGB lighting and efficient airflow, making it ideal for powerful gaming or productivity builds.</p><p>The case comes pre-installed with <strong>four 120 mm RGB fans (three front and one rear)</strong> that provide strong airflow while creating an eye-catching lighting effect inside your system. Its <strong>metal mesh front panel</strong> improves ventilation, helping keep internal components cool even during heavy workloads or gaming sessions. </p><p>A <strong>tempered glass side panel</strong> allows you to showcase your PC components and RGB lighting, giving your setup a premium gaming look. The case supports <strong>ATX, Micro-ATX, and Mini-ITX motherboards</strong>, providing flexibility for a wide range of PC builds. </p><p>For storage and expansion, the chassis includes <strong>2├Ś 3.5-inch HDD bays and 2├Ś 2.5-inch SSD slots</strong>, along with <strong>7 expansion slots</strong> for graphics cards and other components. It also supports GPUs up to <strong>340 mm</strong> in length and CPU coolers up to <strong>165 mm</strong>, making it suitable for modern high-performance hardware.</p>', 25690, 20470, '[]', '[\"Black\"]', '2026-03-09 10:34:05', '[\"[]\"]'),
(73, 'Vivo V70 Smart Phone', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Mobile & Computers', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>6.59-inch 1.5K OLED Display</strong> ŌĆō Smooth <strong>120Hz refresh rate</strong> for vibrant visuals and fluid scrolling. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Snapdragon 7 Gen 4 Processor</strong> ŌĆō Powerful performance for gaming, multitasking, and everyday use. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>50MP ZEISS Telephoto Camera</strong> ŌĆō Advanced portrait and zoom photography with Sony sensor technology. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>50MP Front Camera</strong> ŌĆō High-quality selfies and clear video calls. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>6500mAh Battery</strong> ŌĆō Long-lasting battery with <strong>90W fast charging</strong> support. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>12GB RAM + Up to 512GB Storage</strong> ŌĆō Fast performance with large storage capacity. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>IP68 &amp; IP69 Water/Dust Resistance</strong> ŌĆō Extra durability and protection. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Android 16 with OriginOS 6</strong> ŌĆō Modern interface with improved system performance.</li></ol>', '<p>The <strong>Vivo V70</strong> is a premium smartphone designed for users who want powerful performance, advanced camera capabilities, and a stylish modern design. Built with cutting-edge technology, the device delivers smooth performance, long battery life, and impressive photography features for everyday use. </p><p>The phone features a <strong>6.59-inch AMOLED display</strong> with high resolution and smooth visuals, making it ideal for gaming, streaming, and browsing. Powered by the <strong>Qualcomm Snapdragon 7 Gen 4 processor</strong>, the device ensures fast performance, efficient multitasking, and stable gaming experiences. </p><p>For photography lovers, the Vivo V70 includes a <strong>triple rear camera system with 50MP sensors</strong> that capture detailed photos and professional-style portraits. The <strong>50MP front camera</strong> provides high-quality selfies and video calls, making it perfect for social media and content creation. </p><p>The smartphone is equipped with a <strong>6500mAh battery with 90W fast charging</strong>, allowing you to use the device throughout the day with minimal charging time. With <strong>12GB RAM and up to 512GB storage</strong>, it offers plenty of space and speed for apps, photos, and videos. </p><p>Running on <strong>Android 16 with OriginOS 6</strong>, the Vivo V70 provides a smooth user experience, modern features, and enhanced security updates for long-term reliability.</p>', 160999, 153499, '[]', '[\"Orange\",\"Black\",\"Grey\"]', '2026-03-09 10:39:07', '[\"[]\"]'),
(74, 'Sego Note 80 Smart Phone', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Mobile & Computers', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>6.8ŌĆ│ Large HD+ Display</strong> ŌĆō Immersive visuals for videos and browsing. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>OctaŌĆæCore Processor</strong> ŌĆō Smooth performance for everyday use. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>13 MP Rear Camera</strong> ŌĆō Capture clear photos with AI enhancements. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>8 MP Front Camera</strong> ŌĆō Great for selfies and video calls. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>5000 mAh Battery</strong> ŌĆō Long battery life to stay powered all day. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>128 GB Storage + 12 GB Extended RAM</strong> ŌĆō Lots of space and fluid multitasking. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Dual SIM Support</strong> ŌĆō Convenient for personal &amp; work use. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Runs XAI OS (AndroidŌĆæbased)</strong> ŌĆō UserŌĆæfriendly interface with modern features.</li></ol>', '<p>Discover a smartphone that brings together modern design, smooth performance, and essential features with the <strong>Sego Note 80 Smart Phone</strong>. Designed for everyday users who want reliability and style in one device, this phone offers a balanced experience for browsing, streaming, messaging, and more.</p><p>The Sego Note 80 features a large vibrant display that provides clear visuals for videos, games, and apps. With a responsive processor and sufficient memory, it handles daily tasks with ease while keeping apps running smoothly. Its camera setup lets you capture memorable moments in good detail, whether itŌĆÖs scenic views or selfies with friends.</p><p>Built with a longŌĆælasting battery, the Sego Note 80 keeps you powered through your day without frequent charging. The sleek, modern design adds a touch of sophistication, making it a great choice for users who want dependable performance without compromising on looks.</p><p>Whether youŌĆÖre staying connected with loved ones, streaming your favorite content, or managing everyday tasks, the <strong>Sego Note 80 Smart Phone</strong> offers an enjoyable and dependable mobile experience.</p>', 25000, 22999, '[]', '[\"White\",\"Red\",\"Blue\"]', '2026-03-09 10:42:59', '[\"[]\"]'),
(75, 'Gfive Note 25 Ultra', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Mobile & Computers', '<p><strong>Gfive Note 25 Ultra Smartphone ŌĆō Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Large 6.95ŌĆ│ HD+ Display</strong> ŌĆō Immersive viewing experience for videos and browsing. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Powered by MediaTek Helio G85</strong> ŌĆō Smooth performance for everyday tasks. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>8GB (4+4GB Extended) RAM + 64GB Storage</strong> ŌĆō Good multitasking and ample space; expandable via microSD. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>21 MP Rear Camera</strong> ŌĆō Capture clear photos with LED flash support. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>16 MP Front Camera</strong> ŌĆō Detailed selfies and video calling. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>5000 mAh LongŌĆæLife Battery</strong> ŌĆō AllŌĆæday usage without frequent charging. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Dual 4G SIM Support</strong> ŌĆō Use two networks simultaneously. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Android 14 Operating System</strong> ŌĆō Modern interface and app compatibility. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Side Fingerprint Sensor &amp; Face Unlock</strong> ŌĆō Quick and secure access.</li></ol>', '<p>Experience dependable performance and modern features with the <strong>Gfive Note 25 Ultra Smart Phone</strong>, designed for users who want a seamless mobile experience without compromise. Combining a sleek design with reliable functionality, this smartphone is perfect for daily tasks, entertainment, photography, and staying connected.</p><p>The Gfive Note 25 Ultra features a large, immersive display that brings your photos, videos, and apps to life with vibrant clarity. Its responsive processor and ample memory handle multitasking smoothly, whether youŌĆÖre browsing the web, chatting with friends, or streaming your favorite content. The advanced camera system lets you capture memorable moments with crisp detail, while the front camera is ideal for selfies and video calls.</p>', 26200, 20249, '[]', '[\"Green\",\"Black\"]', '2026-03-09 10:48:24', '[\"[]\"]'),
(76, 'JARS Tourron Matiere Oil Bottle', 'Home Decor', '', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium Quality Material</strong> ŌĆō Durable and elegant design for longŌĆælasting use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Stylish &amp; Modern Look</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for kitchen or dining table display</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>EasyŌĆæPour Spout</strong> ŌĆō Smooth and spillŌĆæfree pouring</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Secure Lid</strong> ŌĆō Keeps oil fresh and prevents leakage</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Large Capacity</strong> ŌĆō Holds ample oil for daily cooking needs</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Ergonomic Handle</strong> ŌĆō Comfortable grip for easy handling</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>MultiŌĆæPurpose Use</strong> ŌĆō Ideal for olive oil, vinegar, sauces, and dressings</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy to Clean</strong> ŌĆō Designed for simple maintenance</li></ol>', '<p>Elevate your kitchen organization with the <strong>JARS Tourron Matiere Oil Bottle</strong>, a premium container designed to store and pour your cooking oils with ease and style. Crafted with highŌĆæquality materials, this oil bottle combines durability with a sleek, modern look that complements any kitchen d├®cor.</p><p>The bottle features a practical shape that fits comfortably in your hand and allows for controlled, dripŌĆæfree pouring ŌĆö perfect for olive oil, vegetable oil, vinegar, or your favorite infused blends. Its secure stopper keeps contents fresh and prevents spills, while the transparent design makes it easy to monitor oil levels at a glance.</p><p>Whether youŌĆÖre drizzling oil over salads, preparing marinades, or simply keeping your countertop organized, the <strong>JARS Tourron Matiere Oil Bottle</strong> offers elegance and utility in one. A mustŌĆæhave for home chefs and everyday cooks alike, it brings convenience and sophistication to your culinary routine.</p>', 890, 750, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 11:01:04', '[\"[]\"]'),
(77, 'JARS Maguelone Creamer', 'Home Decor', '', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>HighŌĆæQuality Ceramic Material</strong> ŌĆō Durable and elegant for everyday use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Classic &amp; Stylish Design</strong> ŌĆō Perfect addition to any table setting</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>EasyŌĆæPour Spout</strong> ŌĆō Smooth and controlled creamer pouring</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Comfortable Handle</strong> ŌĆō Ergonomic grip for ease of use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Perfect Size Capacity</strong> ŌĆō Ideal for serving milk or cream</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Versatile Use</strong> ŌĆō Great for coffee, tea, breakfast, and brunch</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy to Clean</strong> ŌĆō Simple maintenance for daily use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Elegant Gift Option</strong> ŌĆō Stylish and functional for gifting</li></ol>', '<p>Bring charm and practicality to your table with the <strong>JARS Maguelone Creamer</strong>, a beautifully designed piece that combines timeless style with everyday convenience. Perfect for serving cream, milk, or sauces, this creamer adds a touch of sophistication to breakfast, dessert, tea time, or special gatherings.</p><p>Crafted from quality materials, the Maguelone Creamer offers durability and a smooth finish that complements your existing dinnerware. Its ergonomic handle and wellŌĆæshaped spout ensure easy, controlled pouring without drips or spills. Whether youŌĆÖre hosting guests or enjoying a quiet morning coffee, this creamer enhances your dining experience with both style and function.</p><p>Simple yet stylish, the <strong>JARS Maguelone Creamer</strong> is a versatile addition to any kitchen or dining set ŌĆö making everyday moments a little more elegant.</p>', 1200, 1000, '[]', '[\"White\",\"Brown\",\"Yellow\"]', '2026-03-09 12:37:30', '[\"[]\"]'),
(78, 'JARS Maguelone Pitcher', 'Home Decor', '', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium Quality Material</strong> ŌĆō Durable and elegant construction for everyday use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Classic Pitcher Design</strong> ŌĆō Timeless look suitable for any table setting</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Generous Capacity</strong> ŌĆō Ideal for serving water, juice, or beverages</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Ergonomic Handle</strong> ŌĆō Comfortable grip for easy pouring</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>EasyŌĆæPour Spout</strong> ŌĆō Smooth flow with minimal drips</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>MultiŌĆæUse Functionality</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for family meals, parties, and gatherings</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy to Clean</strong> ŌĆō Simple maintenance for frequent use</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Stylish &amp; Functional</strong> ŌĆō Enhances both kitchen and dining presentation</li></ol>', '<p>Serve with elegance using the <strong>JARS Maguelone Pitcher</strong>, a beautifully crafted piece that brings both style and practicality to your table. Whether youŌĆÖre pouring water, juice, iced tea, or other beverages, this pitcher delivers smooth, effortless serving for family meals, gatherings, or special occasions.</p><p>Made from highŌĆæquality materials, the Maguelone Pitcher offers durability with a refined finish that complements any table setting or d├®cor style. Its ergonomic handle provides a comfortable grip, while the wellŌĆædesigned spout ensures clean, dripŌĆæfree pours every time. The classic silhouette and timeless design make it a standout piece thatŌĆÖs both functional and aesthetically pleasing.</p><p>Perfect for everyday use or entertaining guests, the <strong>JARS Maguelone Pitcher</strong> combines versatility, durability, and elegance ŌĆö making every pour a pleasure.</p>', 780, 640, '[]', '[\"White\",\"Green\",\"Brown\",\"Yellow\"]', '2026-03-09 12:44:15', '[\"[]\"]'),
(79, 'COMMUNE Seymour Hand Wash + Reusable Pump 500ml', 'Home Decor', '', '<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(49, 53, 17);\">Elevate your hand care routine with the Seymour Hand Wash + Reusable Pump 500ml. This refillable hand soap is designed with both elegance and sustainability in mind. Housed in a 100% aluminium bottle with a reusable pump that adds sophistication to your space while also reducing plastic waste. Pair it with COMMUNE\'s Double Black Marble Tray or combine it with other Seymour products and reusable containers from the same collection for a sophisticated look and a sustainable approach to body care. </span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(49, 53, 17);\">Inside the box: 1 x Seymour Hand Wash 500ml and 1 x Reusable Pump, both proudly made in the U.K. Add a touch of elegance to your hand care routine and embrace sustainability in style. </span></p>', '<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(49, 53, 17);\">Discover the ultimate sustainable solution with the Seymour Hand Wash Reusable Pump, a stylish and eco-conscious addition to your home or workspace. Thoughtfully designed with both form and function in mind, this durable pump is crafted to minimize single-use plastic waste while delivering an elevated hand care experience. Its sleek, minimalist aesthetic blends effortlessly with modern or classic decor, making it a versatile choice for bathrooms, kitchens, or office spaces.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(49, 53, 17);\">Looking to create a cohesive and luxurious setup? The Seymour Pump pairs perfectly with our Double Black Marble Tray, a sophisticated base that complements its modern design while keeping your space organized and clutter free. For a coordinated look, explore the other Seymour reusable containers within the same collection, ideal for hand wash, lotion, or dish soap. Together, they offer a practical yet elegant solution for maintaining a sustainable and visually appealing home.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(49, 53, 17);\">Make the switch to eco-friendly elegance with the Seymour Hand Wash Reusable Pump. Designed to be as beautiful as it is functional, itŌĆÖs the perfect choice for those who value sustainability without compromising on style.</span></p>', 3800, 3400, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 12:48:58', '[\"[]\"]'),
(80, 'Windrush Stripe Cushion 60x60 Forest Green', 'Home Decor', '', '<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(49, 53, 17);\">Proving that thereŌĆÖs nothing more sophisticated than a stripe, Garden Trading\'s Windrush Stripe cushion adds instant style to any room ŌĆō and to outdoor furniture in the summer. Perfect for styling a sofa, occasional chair, bed or hallway bench, this gorgeous cushion features a heavy weave fabric made from a linen and cotton mix. Complete the look with the matching rectangular version.</span></p>', '<p>Bring a fresh burst of style and comfort to your home with the <strong>Windrush Stripe Cushion 60├Ś60 Forest Green</strong>. Featuring a rich forest green tone paired with classic stripe detailing, this cushion adds both texture and visual interest to any living space. Its generous <strong>60 ├Ś 60 cm size</strong> makes it ideal for sofas, beds, armchairs, or lounge areas, enhancing comfort while elevating the look of your d├®cor.</p><p>Made from soft, durable fabric, this cushion feels inviting against your skin and holds up well to everyday use. The forest green shade introduces a soothing, natureŌĆæinspired accent that complements a wide range of interior styles ŌĆö from contemporary to rustic. Whether placed alone or layered with other cushions, the <strong>Windrush Stripe Cushion</strong> helps create a cozy, welcoming atmosphere in your home.</p>', 1549, 1246, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 12:54:37', '[\"[]\"]');
