(81, 'Ceramic Everything Pot - Werner\'s Nomenclature of Colours', 'Home Decor', '', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium Ceramic Material</strong> ŌĆō Durable stoneware construction for everyday use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Historic Colour Design</strong> ŌĆō Inspired by <em>WernerŌĆÖs Nomenclature of Colours</em>, a famous 19th-century colour guide used by scientists like Charles Darwin. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Elegant Decorative Pattern</strong> ŌĆō Features curated colour swatches adapted from the original 1821 publication by Patrick Syme. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Multi-Purpose Use</strong> ŌĆō Ideal for storing stationery, brushes, kitchen utensils, or as a small plant pot. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Compact Size</strong> ŌĆō Approximately <strong>10 cm height ├Ś 8 cm diameter</strong>, perfect for desks, shelves, or countertops. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Artistic &amp; Vintage Style</strong> ŌĆō Combines historical inspiration with modern home d├®cor.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Handcrafted Finish</strong> ŌĆō Each piece may have slight variations, adding unique character.</li></ol>', '<p>Add a touch of art, history, and practicality to your space with the <strong>Ceramic Everything Pot ŌĆō WernerŌĆÖs Nomenclature of Colours</strong>. This beautifully designed ceramic pot combines decorative charm with everyday functionality, making it perfect for organizing small items or enhancing your home d├®cor.</p><p>Inspired by the historic color reference book <strong>ŌĆ£WernerŌĆÖs Nomenclature of ColoursŌĆØ</strong>, originally published in the early 19th century and famously used by naturalists like <strong>Charles Darwin</strong>, the design features carefully curated color swatches that celebrate the beauty of nature and classic color exploration. </p><p>Crafted from high-quality ceramic, this versatile pot can be used to store stationery, makeup brushes, kitchen utensils, or even as a stylish mini plant holder. Its compact yet functional size makes it ideal for desks, kitchens, shelves, or workspaces, while the unique printed design adds a creative and sophisticated touch to any interior.</p><p>Measuring approximately <strong>10 cm in height and 8 cm in diameter</strong>, the pot offers practical storage while remaining elegant and space-saving. Each piece is carefully crafted, making it both a decorative object and a functional everyday item.</p>', 890, 745, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 15:22:54', '[\"[]\"]'),
(82, 'Garden Trading: Sambourne Doormat, Large', 'Home Decor', '', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Natural Jute Material</strong> ŌĆō Crafted from durable, natural jute fibers for a rustic look. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Large Size (60 ├Ś 90 cm)</strong> ŌĆō Ideal for hallways, entryways, and patio or bifold doors. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Hard-Wearing Design</strong> ŌĆō Built to withstand regular foot traffic while maintaining style. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Unique Natural Texture</strong> ŌĆō Each mat has slight variations due to the natural jute material. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Stylish Decorative Border</strong> ŌĆō Enhances interior d├®cor with a clean, elegant finish. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Indoor Use</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for hallways, utility rooms, or boot rooms. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy Maintenance</strong> ŌĆō Simply vacuum to keep the mat clean. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Slim Profile (1 cm Height)</strong> ŌĆō Fits neatly under most doors without obstruction</li></ol>', '<p>The Garden Trading Sambourne Doormat Large is a stylish and practical indoor doormat designed to bring both durability and natural charm to your home entrance. Woven from <strong>natural, undyed jute</strong>, this mat features a simple yet elegant look that complements a wide range of interior styles, from modern to rustic. </p><p>With its <strong>large 60 cm ├Ś 90 cm size</strong>, the doormat provides generous coverage, making it perfect for hallways, utility rooms, boot rooms, or near sliding and bifold doors. The tough woven jute fibers help capture dirt and debris from shoes, keeping your floors cleaner while maintaining a natural, textured appearance. </p><p>Each mat has slight variations in color and texture because it is made from natural materials, giving every piece a unique character. The durable design ensures long-lasting performance while adding a warm, welcoming touch to your doorway. For safety on smooth floors, using a <strong>non-slip pad underneath</strong> is recommended.</p>', 610, 550, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 15:40:44', '[\"[]\"]'),
(83, 'VT-01 Black Ankle Boots', 'Footwear', 'Casual Shoes', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium Quality Material</strong> ŌĆō Durable upper designed for long-lasting wear.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Classic Black Ankle Design</strong> ŌĆō Stylish look suitable for casual and formal outfits.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Comfortable Cushioned Insole</strong> ŌĆō Provides comfort for all-day walking.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Rubber Sole</strong> ŌĆō Offers good grip and stability on different surfaces.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy Slip-On / Zip Closure</strong> ŌĆō Convenient to wear and remove.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight &amp; Flexible</strong> ŌĆō Ensures comfortable movement throughout the day.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Ankle-Length Support</strong> ŌĆō Provides extra stability and protection around the ankle.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Versatile Fashion Style</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for daily wear, office, or outings.</li></ol>', '<p>Step out with confidence in the <strong>VT-01 Black Ankle Boots</strong>, a stylish footwear choice designed for both fashion and comfort. With their sleek black finish and modern ankle-length design, these boots easily complement a wide range of outfitsŌĆöfrom casual everyday wear to smart-casual or semi-formal looks.</p><p>Crafted from durable materials, the boots provide long-lasting wear while maintaining a polished appearance. The comfortable inner lining and cushioned sole help support your feet throughout the day, making them ideal for work, outings, or evening events. Ankle boots are popular for their versatility and practicality, offering support around the ankle while remaining lightweight and stylish. </p><p>The sturdy outsole provides good traction and stability on different surfaces, while the easy-to-wear design ensures a secure and comfortable fit. Whether paired with jeans, trousers, or dresses, the <strong>VT-01 Black Ankle Boots</strong> add a refined touch to any wardrobe.</p>', 6500, 4999, '[\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 8\",\"US/PAK 7\"]', '[]', '2026-03-09 15:49:57', '[\"[]\"]'),
(84, 'Adi Tokyo - Off White Black', 'Footwear', 'Sneakers', '<p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Key Features:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Premium off-white leather and synthetic upper for durability</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Classic three-stripe design in contrasting black</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Gum rubber outsole for superior traction and vintage aesthetic</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Cushioned insole for enhanced comfort</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Lace-up closure for secure fit</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Lightweight construction for everyday wear</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Versatile colorway pairs with any outfit</span></li></ol>', '<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Step into timeless style with the Adi Tokyo in Off White Black. These premium retro-inspired sneakers blend classic design with modern comfort, making them the perfect choice for both casual wear and athletic activities.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Featuring a sleek off-white leather upper with contrasting black three-stripe detailing, these shoes deliver an iconic look that never goes out of style. The low-profile silhouette and gum rubber outsole provide excellent grip and durability, while the cushioned insole ensures all-day comfort.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Whether you\'re hitting the streets or keeping it casual, the Adi Tokyo Off White Black delivers unmatched style and comfort. Perfect for sneaker enthusiasts who appreciate clean, minimalist design with a retro edge.</span></p>', 14680, 12999, '[\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 8\"]', '[]', '2026-03-09 15:56:29', '[\"[]\"]'),
(85, 'Sk Go Walk V3 - Navy', 'Footwear', 'Sneakers', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight Walking Design</strong> ŌĆō Built for comfortable everyday walking.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Breathable Mesh Upper</strong> ŌĆō Keeps feet cool and comfortable during long wear.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Air-Cooled Memory Foam Insole</strong> ŌĆō Cushioned footbed for superior comfort. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Slip-On Style</strong> ŌĆō Easy to wear with a flexible and convenient design. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Flexible Midsole Cushioning</strong> ŌĆō Helps absorb shock and provides smooth walking. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Rubber Traction Outsole</strong> ŌĆō Improves grip and stability on different surfaces. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Relaxed Fit Design</strong> ŌĆō Extra room at the toe and forefoot for comfort. </li></ol>', '<p>Step into everyday comfort with the <strong>Skechers GO Walk V3 ŌĆō Navy</strong>, a lightweight walking shoe designed for people who want cushioning, flexibility, and easy wear. Known for its sporty design and relaxed fit, this shoe is perfect for daily walking, casual outings, or long hours on your feet.</p><p>The shoe features a <strong>breathable mesh upper</strong> combined with a flexible slip-on design that provides a comfortable, sock-like fit. Inside, the <strong>Air-Cooled Memory Foam insole</strong> delivers soft cushioning and breathability, helping keep your feet comfortable throughout the day. </p><p>The <strong>lightweight midsole cushioning</strong> helps absorb shock while walking, and the flexible outsole provides traction and stability on different surfaces. With its sleek navy color and minimal design, the GO Walk V3 pairs easily with jeans, joggers, or casual outfits.</p>', 7999, 6999, '[\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 8\"]', '[]', '2026-03-09 16:15:16', '[\"[]\"]'),
(86, 'Pma Park Sneakers - Black White Gum', 'Footwear', 'Sneakers', '<p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Key Features:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Colorway:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Black/White/Gum - a versatile combination that pairs effortlessly with any outfit</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Upper Construction:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Premium black leather and suede panels for durability and premium feel</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Signature Branding:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Oversized white Pma Formstrip logo on lateral and medial sides</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Outsole:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Gum rubber outsole with herringbone traction pattern for superior grip</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Midsole:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Black platform-style midsole for added comfort and modern silhouette</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Tongue &amp; Collar:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Padded construction with Pma branding for comfort and style</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Lacing System:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Traditional lace-up closure with tonal black laces</span></li></ol>', '<p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Premium Streetwear Meets Classic Court Style</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The Pma Park Sneakers deliver timeless skate-inspired design with modern comfort. Featuring a sleek black leather and suede upper contrasted by bold white Pma branding, these sneakers strike the perfect balance between heritage aesthetics and contemporary streetwear appeal.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Design Details:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> The contrast between the all-black upper and the natural gum outsole creates a clean, sophisticated look that works equally well on the street or in casual settings. The chunky platform sole adds a contemporary edge while maintaining the classic court shoe DNA.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Styling Versatility:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Perfect for streetwear enthusiasts who appreciate clean, minimalist design with bold branding. These sneakers complement everything from joggers and denim to casual workwear.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Comfort &amp; Performance:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Built for all-day wear with cushioned insoles and supportive construction that doesn\'t sacrifice style for comfort.</span></p>', 11999, 9999, '[\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 8\"]', '[]', '2026-03-09 16:21:26', '[\"[]\"]'),
(87, 'Nirvana Lady Nirvana', 'Bags & Accessories', 'Crossbody Bags', '<p><strong>Key Features </strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight Walking Design</strong> ŌĆō Built for comfortable everyday walking.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Breathable Mesh Upper</strong> ŌĆō Keeps feet cool and comfortable during long wear.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Air-Cooled Memory Foam Insole</strong> ŌĆō Cushioned footbed for superior comfort. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Slip-On Style</strong> ŌĆō Easy to wear with a flexible and convenient design. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Flexible Midsole Cushioning</strong> ŌĆō Helps absorb shock and provides smooth walking. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Rubber Traction Outsole</strong> ŌĆō Improves grip and stability on different surfaces. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Relaxed Fit Design</strong> ŌĆō Extra room at the toe and forefoot for comfort. </li></ol>', '<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Timeless sophistication. The Crossbody\'s sophisticated design will quickly become a \"must-have\" bag. It complements all the ultra-feminine trends of the season.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Leather Description</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">: </span></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Cow premium quality Milled grain (Tan Brown, Black, yellow)</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Cow premium Quality leather (Blue)</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Cow premium quality Croc Embossed (Navy Blue)</span></li></ol><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Pockets:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\"> Inside Nylon Zippered and open pocket</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Accessories: </strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Fixed Shoulder Handle,</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Single Compartment,</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">High-quality YKK Metal zipper,</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Top Tech Lining,</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Shiny Nickel Accessories.</span></li></ol><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Dimension (Inch):</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=