(88, 'Nirvana Strip Wallet', 'Bags & Accessories', 'Wallet', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Multiple Card Slots</strong> ŌĆō Includes <strong>six credit card slots</strong> for easy organization of cards. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Dual Cash Compartments</strong> ŌĆō Two spacious sections to keep cash neatly separated. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Two ID Windows</strong> ŌĆō Convenient display slots for ID cards or licenses. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Extra Flap Storage</strong> ŌĆō Additional pockets for receipts and extra cards. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Compact &amp; Slim Design</strong> ŌĆō Approx. <strong>3.5 ├Ś 4.5 inches</strong>, perfect for pockets. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Elegant Strip Style</strong> ŌĆō Modern design suitable for everyday use or formal occasions.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Bonus Accessory</strong> ŌĆō Comes with a matching leather keychain.</li></ol>', '<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Cow Premium Quality Semi-Veg tanned Leather (Black)</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Cow Premium Quality Glaze Finish Leather (Tan)</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Pockets:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Two Cash Compartment, Two ID Window, Six Credit Card Slots, Two pockets for cards/receipts</span></p><h6><strong style=\"background-color: rg