d </span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Hyaluronic Acid</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">, helps to reduce dark spots, hyperpigmentation, and uneven skin tone. Perfect for all skin types, it delivers instant radiance and a smoother, revitalized texture, making it the ideal addition to your skincare routine.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Research Results: 97% </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">reported improved &amp; brighter skin texture &amp; softer, more supple skin</span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">* 94%</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\"> felt it had decreased rough patches</span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">* 88%</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\"> noticed soothed skin that felt silky &amp; velvety</span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">* 85%</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\"> said their skin was radiant</span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">*</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Ingredients:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Grapefruit, Lemon, Almond, Saffron, Rose, Sweet Orange, AHA/BHA, Facial Anti-Oxidants, Kojic Acid, Alpha Arbutin, Salicylic Acid, Hyaluronic Acid, Vitamin C</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">How to Use:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Apply a generous amount to clean, damp skin. Leave on for 7 - 8 minutes to allow the formula to work. Gently massage in circular motions to exfoliate, then rinse off with lukewarm water. Can use 3 ŌĆō 4 times a week.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">This brightening polish isnŌĆÖt just a skincare product ŌĆō itŌĆÖs your shortcut to a flawless, glowing complexion. Perfect before makeup or as a weekly skin detox.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">???? </span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(81, 81, 103);\">Stock is running low ŌĆō grab yours now and glow up while supplies last!</strong></p>', 1999, 1499, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 16:52:39', '[\"[]\"]'),
(91, 'Extreme Brightening Cream', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Skin Treatments', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Intense Skin Brightening:</strong> Reduces dullness and promotes a visibly radiant complexion.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Evens Skin Tone:</strong> Helps minimize dark spots, pigmentation, and uneven skin patches.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Deep Hydration:</strong> Moisturizes skin for a soft, supple, and healthy feel.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Gentle on Skin:</strong> Dermatologically tested formula suitable for daily use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Enhances Natural Glow:</strong> Restores skinŌĆÖs natural luminosity and freshness.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight &amp; Non-Greasy:</strong> Absorbs quickly without leaving sticky residue.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Boosts Skin Radiance:</strong> Helps skin look brighter, smoother, and rejuvenated.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Protects Skin Texture:</strong> Strengthens skin barrier for long-lasting softness and glow.</li></ol>', '<p>Reveal a brighter, more luminous complexion with <strong>Extreme Brightening Cream</strong>, specially formulated to target dullness, uneven skin tone, and pigmentation. Enriched with potent brightening ingredients, this cream helps reduce dark spots and promotes a more radiant, glowing appearance.</p><p>Its lightweight, fast-absorbing formula nourishes the skin while improving texture and softness. Suitable for daily use, the cream hydrates deeply without leaving a greasy residue, making it ideal for all skin types. Regular use helps restore skinŌĆÖs natural glow, leaving it looking healthy, smooth, and visibly brighter.</p><p>Perfect for those seeking a convenient solution to dull or uneven skin, <strong>Extreme Brightening Cream</strong> combines care, hydration, and brightening benefits in one daily skincare essential.</p>', 2549, 1912, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 17:45:16', '[\"[]\"]'),
(93, 'Vox | R-7085 Airpods', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Audio & Accessories', '<p><strong>Key Features ŌĆō Vox R-7085 AirPods</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>High-Quality Sound:</strong> Crisp treble and deep bass for an immersive audio experience.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Wireless Convenience:</strong> True wireless design for tangle-free listening.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Long Battery Life:</strong> Up to several hours of continuous play with quick recharge case.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Ergonomic Fit:</strong> Comfortable in-ear design suitable for extended wear.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy Connectivity:</strong> Fast pairing with smartphones, tablets, and other Bluetooth devices.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Built-in Microphone:</strong> Clear voice calls and hands-free operation.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Portable Charging Case:</strong> Compact case ensures your AirPods stay charged on the go.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Touch Controls:</strong> Intuitive touch interface for music, calls, and voice assistant access.</li></ol>', '<p>Enjoy freedom from wires and quality sound on the go with the <strong>Vox RŌĆæ7085 AirPods</strong>, designed for comfort, convenience, and everyday listening. These sleek wireless earbuds combine modern style with reliable performance, making them a great choice for music, calls, and handsŌĆæfree convenience.</p><p>Featuring wireless Bluetooth connectivity, the Vox RŌĆæ7085 AirPods let you pair easily with your smartphone, tablet, or other compatible devices. The ergonomic design ensures a comfortable fit for long listening sessions, while the secure inŌĆæear build helps keep them in place during movement.</p><p>The earbuds deliver clear, balanced audio thatŌĆÖs perfect for streaming music, podcasts, or taking calls on the move. With intuitive touch controls, you can play/pause tracks, adjust volume, or answer calls without needing to reach for your device. The compact charging case provides extra battery life and makes it easy to take your AirPods wherever you go.</p><p>Whether youŌĆÖre commuting, working out, or just relaxing, the <strong>Vox RŌĆæ7085 AirPods</strong> offer stylish design, dependable connectivity, and quality sound in a wireless package that fits your lifestyle.</p>', 8595, 6995, '[]', '[\"Blue\",\"Grey\"]', '2026-03-09 18:02:31', '[\"[]\"]'),
