style=\"color: rgb(35, 47, 95); background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">2 x 10W</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(35, 47, 95); background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">Dolby Digital</span></p>', 82000, 75000, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-09 18:11:51', '[\"[]\"]');
INSERT INTO `products` (`_id`, `name`, `category`, `subCategory`, `about`, `description`, `price`, `offerPrice`, `footwear_sizes`, `colors`, `created_at`, `sizes`) VALUES
(96, 'Flyknit West Piana Sneakers', 'Footwear', 'Sneakers', '<h3><strong>Key Features</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Breathable Flyknit Upper</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span> Engineered knit material allows maximum airflow, keeping your feet cool and sweat-free all day. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight Comfort</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span> Ultra-light construction reduces foot fatigue, giving you a smooth and effortless walking experience. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Cushioned Footbed</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span> Soft and responsive cushioning provides superior comfort with every step. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Flexible &amp; Natural Movement</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span> Designed to adapt to your foot shape, offering a sock-like fit and natural motion support. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Outsole Grip</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span> High-quality outsole ensures excellent traction and long-lasting performance on various surfaces. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>All-Weather Wearability</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span> Perfect for daily use in different weather conditions without compromising comfort. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Modern &amp; Versatile Design</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span> Sleek, stylish look suitable for casual outings, travel, or everyday wear.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Snug Sock-Like Fit</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span> Stretchable knit structure hugs your feet for a secure and comfortable fit.</li></ol>', '<p>Step into effortless comfort and contemporary style with the <strong>Flyknit West Piana Sneakers</strong>. Designed for everyday wear, these sneakers feature a breathable flyknit upper that keeps your feet cool and fresh throughout the day. The flexible, sock-like fit adapts to your foot shape, providing a snug yet comfortable feel with every step.</p><p>Built with lightweight materials, these sneakers reduce fatigue, making them perfect for long walks, casual outings, or daily routines. The cushioned footbed offers superior support and shock absorption, while the durable outsole ensures reliable grip on multiple surfaces.</p><p>Whether you\'re heading out for a busy day or keeping it casual, the sleek and versatile design of the Flyknit West Piana Sneakers makes them an ideal choice for any occasion.</p>', 14999, 12999, '[\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 8\",\"US/PAK 7\",\"US/PAK 6\"]', '[]', '2026-03-17 09:36:30', '[]'),
(97, 'Peshawari Sleek For Men', 'Footwear', 'Casual Shoes', '<h3>Ō£© Key Features ŌĆō Peshawari Sleek</h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Modern Slim Design</strong> ŌĆō A refined and sleek silhouette that gives a contemporary twist to the traditional Peshawari style.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium Quality Material</strong> ŌĆō Crafted with high-grade leather for durability and long-lasting wear.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Comfort-Focused Build</strong> ŌĆō Soft inner lining and cushioned sole ensure all-day comfort.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Versatile Wear</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for both casual outings and semi-formal occasions.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Handcrafted Finish</strong> ŌĆō Expert craftsmanship with attention to detail for a premium look.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Secure Fit</strong> ŌĆō Adjustable strap design for a snug and customized fit.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Sole</strong> ŌĆō Strong and anti-slip sole for better grip and stability.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Breathable Design</strong> ŌĆō Keeps your feet cool and comfortable even in warm weather.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight Feel</strong> ŌĆō Easy to wear for long hours without fatigue.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Elegant Look</strong> ŌĆō Minimalist yet stylish design that complements eastern wear.</li></ol>', '<p>Step into a legacy of tradition redefined for the modern era with the <strong>Peshawari Sleek</strong>. Rooted in the rich cultural heritage of South Asia, this refined version of the classic Peshawari chappal is designed for individuals who value timeless craftsmanship while embracing a clean, contemporary aesthetic.</p><p>Expertly crafted from high-quality materials, the Peshawari Sleek delivers both durability and sophistication. The smooth, polished finish enhances its premium look, while the structured yet flexible design ensures a comfortable fit that adapts naturally to your feet. Every detail, from the fine stitching to the carefully shaped silhouette, reflects superior workmanship and attention to detail.</p><p>Unlike traditional bulky designs, the Peshawari Sleek features a streamlined profile that adds a modern touch without losing its authentic essence. The soft inner lining provides all-day comfort, making it suitable for extended wear during events, gatherings, or daily routines. Its sturdy outsole offers reliable grip and stability, ensuring confidence with every step you take.</p><p>Versatility is at the heart of this design. Whether paired with traditional attire like shalwar kameez or styled with smart casual outfits, the Peshawari Sleek effortlessly enhances your overall look. It transitions seamlessly from festive occasions to formal settings and even casual outings, making it a dependable choice for any wardrobe.</p><p>This is more than just footwearŌĆöitŌĆÖs a statement of style, culture, and confidence. The Peshawari Sleek embodies the perfect balance between heritage and innovation, giving you a product that feels as good as it looks.</p>', 10189, 8199, '[\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 8\"]', '[]', '2026-03-17 09:53:59', '[]'),
(98, 'Extra Support Alf Roma Slippers', 'Footwear', 'Casual Shoes', '<h3><strong>Ō£© Key Features</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Enhanced Arch Support</strong> ŌĆō Specially designed to provide extra support for your feet, reducing strain and improving comfort.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Ergonomic Design</strong> ŌĆō Contours to the natural shape of your foot for better posture and stability.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium Build Quality</strong> ŌĆō Made with durable and high-quality materials for long-lasting use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Ultra-Comfort Cushioning</strong> ŌĆō Soft padded footbed absorbs shock and ensures all-day comfort.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Anti-Slip Sole</strong> ŌĆō Strong grip outsole prevents slipping on smooth surfaces.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight Construction</strong> ŌĆō Easy to wear for extended periods without fatigue.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Breathable Upper</strong> ŌĆō Keeps feet cool and fresh, ideal for daily wear.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy Slip-On Style</strong> ŌĆō Convenient design for quick wear and removal.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Versatile Usage</strong> ŌĆō Suitable for home, casual outings, and daily wear.</li></ol>', '<p>Redefine everyday comfort with the <strong>Extra Support Alf Roma Slippers</strong>, thoughtfully designed for those who prioritize both relaxation and reliable foot support. Whether you\'re at home, running quick errands, or stepping out casually, these slippers provide the perfect balance of softness, stability, and durability.</p><p>Crafted with high-quality materials, the Alf Roma Slippers feature a supportive structure that helps reduce foot strain and enhances overall comfort. The ergonomically designed footbed contours naturally to your feet, offering excellent arch support and cushioning with every step. This makes them an ideal choice for prolonged wear, ensuring your feet stay relaxed and well-supported throughout the day.</p><p>The upper is designed for a secure yet breathable fit, allowing proper airflow while keeping your feet comfortably in place. Inside, the soft lining adds an extra layer of coziness, making each step feel smooth and gentle. Unlike ordinary slippers, the Extra Support Alf Roma is built to provide enhanced stability, helping you walk with confidence on various surfaces.</p><p>Its durable outsole delivers reliable grip and traction, reducing the risk of slipping while ensuring long-lasting performance. The sleek and minimal design adds a modern touch, making these slippers versatile enough to pair with both indoor and outdoor casual wear.</p>', 7200, 5499, '[\"US/PAK 8\",\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 7\",\"US/PAK 6\"]', '[]', '2026-03-17 10:59:18', '[]'),
(99, 'Bounce 3 Straps Bernard Sandals', 'Footwear', 'Casual Shoes', '<h3><strong>Ō£© Key Features</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Triple Strap Design</strong> ŌĆō Secure 3-strap construction for a firm, adjustable, and stylish fit.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Bounce Cushion Technology</strong> ŌĆō Responsive cushioned sole that absorbs impact and provides superior comfort.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Ergonomic Footbed</strong> ŌĆō Designed to support natural foot shape for enhanced stability and ease.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Build</strong> ŌĆō High-quality materials ensure long-lasting performance and daily reliability.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Anti-Slip Outsole</strong> ŌĆō Textured sole offers excellent grip on different surfaces.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Breathable Comfort</strong> ŌĆō Open design allows airflow to keep feet cool and fresh.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight Feel</strong> ŌĆō Easy to wear all day without discomfort or heaviness.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Adjustable Fit</strong> ŌĆō Flexible straps provide a customized and secure fit.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Versatile Style</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for casual wear, outdoor use, and everyday activities.</li></ol>', '<p>Step into all-day ease and modern functionality with the <strong>Bounce 3 Straps Bernard Sandals</strong>. Designed for active lifestyles and everyday wear, these sandals combine superior cushioning with a secure, adjustable fitŌĆömaking them the perfect companion for both casual outings and on-the-go routines.</p><p>Featuring a three-strap design, these sandals provide enhanced stability and a customized fit that adapts to your foot shape. The adjustable straps ensure a snug and supportive feel, keeping your feet firmly in place while allowing natural movement. Whether you\'re walking, traveling, or simply relaxing, youŌĆÖll experience unmatched comfort with every step.</p><p>At the core of the design is the responsive ŌĆ£BounceŌĆØ cushioning technology, engineered to absorb impact and deliver a soft, energized feel underfoot. The contoured footbed supports your arches and reduces pressure, helping minimize fatigue even during extended wear.</p>', 10999, 8900, '[\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 8\",\"US/PAK 7\"]', '[\"Black\",\"Brown\"]', '2026-03-17 11:07:08', '[]'),
(100, 'Breathable Speed Arrow Sneakers', 'Footwear', 'Sneakers', '<h3><strong>Ō£© Key Features</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Ultra-Breathable Mesh</strong> ŌĆō Keeps your feet cool and sweat-free during long hours of wear.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight Performance</strong> ŌĆō Designed for effortless movement and all-day comfort.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Ergonomic Cushioning</strong> ŌĆō Soft, responsive midsole absorbs impact for smooth walking or running.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Outsole</strong> ŌĆō High-traction sole ensures grip and stability on various surfaces.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Sleek, Modern Design</strong> ŌĆō Stylish look suitable for casual wear, sports, and active lifestyles.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Flexible Fit</strong> ŌĆō Adaptive structure conforms to your foot shape for better support.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Quick-Lace System</strong> ŌĆō Easy to put on and adjust for a secure fit.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Shock Absorption</strong> ŌĆō Reduces pressure on feet during high-impact activities.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight &amp; Breathable</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for gym, outdoor runs, or daily use.</li></ol>', '<p>Elevate your performance and everyday style with the <strong>Breathable Speed Arrow Sneakers</strong>. Engineered for speed, comfort, and versatility, these sneakers are perfect for active lifestyles, casual outings, or long walks. Combining modern design with functional technology, they keep you moving effortlessly while ensuring your feet stay cool and supported.</p><p>The sneakers feature a <strong>breathable upper</strong> that promotes maximum airflow, helping to keep your feet fresh and dry even during extended wear. The lightweight construction reduces fatigue, allowing you to stay on your feet longer without discomfort. A <strong>cushioned midsole</strong> provides responsive support and shock absorption, making each step smooth and energizing.</p><p>Designed with a <strong>flexible outsole</strong>, the Speed Arrow adapts to your natural foot movements, giving you superior traction and stability on various surfaces. The sleek, aerodynamic silhouette adds a sporty, contemporary look, making these sneakers versatile enough to pair with athletic wear or casual outfits.</p>', 15780, 13999, '[\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 8\",\"US/PAK 7\"]', '[\"White\",\"Green\",\"Black\"]', '2026-03-17 11:12:57', '[]'),
(101, 'Rush Lead Sneakers For Men', 'Footwear', 'Sneakers', '<h3><strong>Ō£© Key Features</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Modern Athletic Design</strong> ŌĆō Stylish silhouette perfect for casual, sporty, or everyday wear.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight Construction</strong> ŌĆō Comfortable for all-day use without feeling heavy on your feet.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Breathable Upper</strong> ŌĆō Ensures proper airflow, keeping feet cool and fresh.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Cushioned Insole</strong> ŌĆō Soft padding provides shock absorption and all-day comfort.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Rubber Outsole</strong> ŌĆō Anti-slip sole for superior traction and stability on multiple surfaces.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Flexible Fit</strong> ŌĆō Adapts to your foot shape for natural movement and support.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Secure Lace Closure</strong> ŌĆō Easy to adjust for a snug and customized fit.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Versatile Wear</strong> ŌĆō Ideal for sports, casual outings, or daily use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Impact-Resistant Sole</strong> ŌĆō Reduces foot fatigue during long walks or active sessions.</li></ol>', '<p>Step up your game with the <strong>Rush Lead Sneakers For Men</strong>, designed for men who demand style, comfort, and durability in one sleek package. Perfect for casual outings, active lifestyles, or everyday wear, these sneakers are engineered to provide a supportive fit, lightweight performance, and modern aesthetics.</p><p>The <strong>premium upper material</strong> ensures breathability and flexibility, keeping your feet cool and comfortable throughout the day. The <strong>ergonomic cushioned insole</strong> offers excellent arch support and shock absorption, reducing fatigue and providing all-day comfortŌĆöeven during long walks or busy schedules.</p><p>Built with a <strong>durable outsole</strong>, the Rush Lead Sneakers deliver superior traction and stability on a variety of surfaces. Their lightweight construction allows for natural movement, while the streamlined design adds a contemporary, sporty look to any outfit.</p>', 20199, 17999, '[\"US/PAK 11\",\"US/PAK 10\",\"US/PAK 9\",\"US/PAK 8\",\"US/PAK 7\"]', '[\"White\",\"Black\",\"Grey\"]', '2026-03-17 11:19:08', '[]'),
