(111, ' Louis Vuitton 1969 Monogram Canvas Pochette Felicie Wallets', 'Bags & Accessories', 'Wallet', '<h3><strong>Key Features </strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Iconic Monogram Canvas</strong> ŌĆō Timeless Louis Vuitton pattern that exudes luxury and sophistication.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium Craftsmanship</strong> ŌĆō Made with high-quality materials and meticulous attention to detail.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Compact &amp; Elegant Design</strong> ŌĆō Sleek silhouette perfect for carrying essentials in style.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Multiple Compartments</strong> ŌĆō Organized storage for cards, cash, and small personal items.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Secure Closure</strong> ŌĆō Snap or zipper closure ensures valuables are safely stored.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight &amp; Portable</strong> ŌĆō Easy to carry in hand or as a mini clutch for outings.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Versatile Use</strong> ŌĆō Can be used as a wallet, small clutch, or inside a larger bag.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Hardware</strong> ŌĆō Gold-tone fittings and smooth finishes for long-lasting elegance.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Luxury Statement Piece</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for fashion-forward users and collectors.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Timeless Style</strong> ŌĆō Combines classic Louis Vuitton design with modern functionality.</li></ol>', '<p>Elevate your accessory game with the <strong>Louis Vuitton 1969 Monogram Canvas Pochette Felicie Wallet</strong>, a perfect fusion of heritage, elegance, and modern functionality. Designed for women who appreciate sophistication and authenticity, this wallet is more than just an accessoryŌĆöitŌĆÖs a statement of timeless luxury.</p><p>Crafted from <strong>premium Louis Vuitton monogram canvas</strong>, this wallet showcases the iconic pattern that has become synonymous with elegance and style. The refined craftsmanship, from meticulous stitching to polished hardware, ensures durability while maintaining a luxurious feel.</p><p>Featuring a <strong>compact yet versatile design</strong>, the Pochette Felicie allows you to carry your essentials in style. Multiple compartments and card slots provide organized space for cards, cash, and small personal items, keeping everything accessible and neatly arranged. Its sleek silhouette allows it to double as a clutch or to be tucked inside a larger handbag, offering flexibility for every occasion.</p><p>The walletŌĆÖs <strong>classic design and iconic branding</strong> make it perfect for formal events, casual outings, or daily use. Lightweight and stylish, it combines practicality with prestige, ensuring that you carry your essentials with confidence and sophistication.</p>', 7500, 6000, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 12:52:27', '[]');
