(112, 'Golden Latest Stylo Bridal Clutch For Women 5002', 'Bags & Accessories', 'Wallet', '<h3><strong>Ō£© Key Features </strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Elegant Bridal Design</strong> ŌĆō Stunning golden finish perfect for weddings, parties, and special occasions.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium Craftsmanship</strong> ŌĆō High-quality materials with intricate detailing and a polished look.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Compact &amp; Stylish</strong> ŌĆō Sleek silhouette that fits essentials like phone, cards, and lipstick.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Secure Closure</strong> ŌĆō Reliable clasp or zipper keeps belongings safe.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight &amp; Portable</strong> ŌĆō Comfortable to carry throughout events without hassle.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Versatile Carrying Options</strong> ŌĆō Can be hand-held or worn using a detachable chain strap.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Build</strong> ŌĆō Strong materials and hardware ensure long-lasting use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Sparkling Finish</strong> ŌĆō Eye-catching shine and embellishments that complement bridal outfits.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Sophisticated Appeal</strong> ŌĆō Adds a glamorous touch to ethnic or western attire.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Perfect Gift Option</strong> ŌĆō Ideal for gifting on weddings, anniversaries, or festive occasions.</li></ol>', '<p>Make every celebration unforgettable with the <strong>Golden Latest Stylo Bridal Clutch For Women 5002</strong>, designed to add a touch of sparkle and sophistication to your bridal or party ensemble. Perfect for weddings, engagements, or festive occasions, this clutch combines exquisite design with practical functionality.</p><p>Crafted with <strong>premium materials</strong> and adorned with shimmering golden accents, the Stylo Bridal Clutch exudes elegance and luxury. Its compact yet spacious interior provides enough room to carry your essentials such as a phone, lipstick, cards, and small personal items, keeping everything organized while maintaining a sleek silhouette.</p><p>The clutch features a <strong>secure clasp closure</strong> and a stylish, structured design that enhances its chic appearance. Lightweight and easy to carry, it is perfect for pairing with traditional bridal attire, evening gowns, or party dresses. Its glittering golden finish ensures you shine at every event, making it a must-have accessory for women who love glamour and style.</p><p>Whether for weddings, parties, or festive gatherings, the <strong>Golden Latest Stylo Bridal Clutch 5002</strong> is a perfect combination of elegance, functionality, and sophistication.</p>', 25000, 2399, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 12:57:31', '[]'),
(113, 'Baellerry Letter Patched Detail Colorblock Chain Phone Wallet 6003', 'Bags & Accessories', 'Wallet', '<h3><strong>Ō£© Key Features</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Trendy Colorblock Design</strong> ŌĆō Stylish combination of colors with eye-catching contrast.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Letter Patch Detail</strong> ŌĆō Modern branded patch adds a fashionable and premium touch.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium PU Leather</strong> ŌĆō Durable, smooth, and easy-to-clean material for everyday use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Multi-Functional Wallet</strong> ŌĆō Combines phone holder, wallet, and mini handbag in one.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Spacious Compartments</strong> ŌĆō Multiple slots for cards, cash, and essentials.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Secure Closure</strong> ŌĆō Zipper and snap design keeps your belongings safe.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Detachable Chain Strap</strong> ŌĆō Can be used as a crossbody, shoulder bag, or clutch.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight &amp; Portable</strong> ŌĆō Easy to carry for shopping, travel, or daily outings.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Smooth Zippers &amp; Hardware</strong> ŌĆō High-quality fittings ensure durability and ease of use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Chic &amp; Versatile Style</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for casual, party, and on-the-go fashion needs.</li></ol>', '<p>Upgrade your everyday essentials with the <strong>Baellerry Letter Patched Detail Colorblock Chain Phone Wallet 6003</strong>, a perfect blend of fashion, convenience, and modern design. Crafted for women who love stylish yet practical accessories, this wallet is designed to keep your essentials organized while adding a bold statement to your look.</p><p>Featuring a <strong>unique colorblock design with letter patch detailing</strong>, this wallet stands out with its trendy and eye-catching appeal. Made from <strong>high-quality materials</strong>, it offers durability and a smooth finish, ensuring long-lasting use without compromising on style.</p><p>The wallet is designed with a <strong>spacious interior layout</strong>, including multiple card slots, cash compartments, and a dedicated section for your smartphone. This all-in-one design allows you to carry your phone, money, and essentials securely in one compact accessory. The <strong>secure zip and snap closure</strong> keeps your belongings safe and organized throughout the day.</p><p>Equipped with a <strong>stylish chain strap</strong>, it can be used as a crossbody bag or carried as a clutch, giving you versatility for different occasions. Whether you\'re heading out for shopping, traveling, or casual outings, this wallet offers hands-free convenience with a fashionable touch.</p>', 1200, 999, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 13:02:34', '[]'),
(114, 'Crossbody Bag Wallet for Women 2028', 'Bags & Accessories', 'Wallet', '<h3><strong>Key Features </strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Stylish &amp; Modern Design</strong> ŌĆō Sleek look that complements casual, office, and party outfits.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Premium Material</strong> ŌĆō Durable PU leather or high-quality fabric for long-lasting use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Multi-Functional</strong> ŌĆō Combines wallet and crossbody bag for convenient storage.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Spacious Interior</strong> ŌĆō Holds phone, cards, cash, and other essentials securely.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Multiple Compartments</strong> ŌĆō Organized slots for easy access and tidy storage.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Secure Closure</strong> ŌĆō Reliable zipper or magnetic snap keeps belongings safe.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Adjustable Crossbody Strap</strong> ŌĆō Comfortable, customizable fit for all-day wear.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight &amp; Portable</strong> ŌĆō Easy to carry without adding bulk.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Durable Hardware</strong> ŌĆō Smooth zippers and strong fittings for enhanced longevity.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Versatile &amp; Practical</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for shopping, travel, work, or daily outings.</li></ol>', '<p>Keep your essentials organized and your hands free with the <strong>Crossbody Bag Wallet for Women 2028</strong>. Designed for modern women who value both style and practicality, this versatile accessory combines the functionality of a wallet with the convenience of a crossbody bag.</p><p>Crafted from <strong>high-quality, durable materials</strong>, this bag ensures long-lasting use while maintaining a sleek, polished appearance. Its <strong>compact yet spacious design</strong> features multiple compartments for cards, cash, phone, and small personal items, keeping everything organized and easily accessible.</p><p>The adjustable <strong>crossbody strap</strong> allows for a comfortable, customizable fit, making it perfect for daily use, shopping trips, travel, or casual outings. A secure zip closure keeps your belongings safe while the lightweight construction ensures effortless carrying throughout the day.</p><p>With a <strong>modern, minimalist design</strong>, the Crossbody Bag Wallet for Women 2028 complements a wide range of outfitsŌĆöfrom casual daywear to semi-formal ensembles. Practical, stylish, and versatile, itŌĆÖs an essential accessory for women on the go.</p>', 4000, 3500, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 13:05:57', '[]'),
(115, 'Best Face Whitening Face Wash - Beads 120ml with Kojic Acid & Vitamin C', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Skin Treatments', '<h3><strong>Ō£© Key Features</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Advanced Whitening Formula</strong> ŌĆō Infused with <strong>Kojic Acid &amp; Vitamin C</strong> to brighten and even out skin tone.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Exfoliating Beads</strong> ŌĆō Gentle micro-beads help remove dirt, dead skin cells, and impurities for a smooth complexion.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Deep Cleansing</strong> ŌĆō Effectively cleanses pores, reduces excess oil, and prevents breakouts.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Hydrating &amp; Nourishing</strong> ŌĆō Enriched with vitamins to maintain skin moisture and softness.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Gentle on Skin</strong> ŌĆō Suitable for daily use on all skin types without causing irritation.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Radiance Boost</strong> ŌĆō Regular use improves skin texture and gives a natural glow.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Antioxidant Protection</strong> ŌĆō Vitamin C helps protect skin from free radicals and environmental damage.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Refreshing Fragrance</strong> ŌĆō Leaves a pleasant and invigorating scent after every wash.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Compact &amp; Travel-Friendly</strong> ŌĆō 120ml size is convenient for home or on-the-go use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditab