><u style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(12, 169, 106);\">collagen</u><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> production.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(12, 169, 106);\">Vitamin C: A potent antioxidant that evens skin</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> tone and protects against environmental damage.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(12, 169, 106);\">Vitamin E:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(12, 169, 106);\"> Moisturizes and soothes the skin</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">, enhancing overall texture and radiance.</span></li></ol><h2><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Gentle Exfoliation for a Smooth Complexion:</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Infused with gentle exfoliating beads, Beads Whitening Face Wash removes dead skin cells, revealing smoother and healthier-looking skin. With regular use, it promotes an even skin tone and a natural glow.</span></p><h3><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Why Choose Beads Whitening Face Wash?</span></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Dermatologist-Tested:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> </span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(12, 169, 106);\">Safe for all skin types</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">, including </span><u style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(12, 169, 106);\">sensitive skin</u><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(12, 169, 106);\">Daily Use Formula: Lightweight</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> and effective for morning and evening routines.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Authentic Product:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> Available exclusively at </span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">derma.pk</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">, PakistanŌĆÖs trusted online pharmacy.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Nationwide Delivery:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> Enjoy convenient and reliable delivery to your doorstep.</span></li></ol><h3><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">How to Use:</span></h3><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Wet your face with lukewarm water.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Apply a small amount of Beads Whitening </span><u style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(12