 even complexion with the <strong>DarkOut Skin Brightening Cream (30g)</strong>. Specially formulated to target dark spots, pigmentation, and uneven skin tone, this advanced skincare solution helps restore your skinŌĆÖs natural glow with consistent use.</p><p>Enriched with <strong>skin-brightening and nourishing ingredients</strong>, DarkOut Cream works deep within the skin to reduce the appearance of blemishes, sun damage, and discoloration. Its gentle yet effective formula promotes a clearer, more balanced look while maintaining essential hydration for soft and healthy skin.</p><p>The <strong>lightweight, non-greasy texture</strong> absorbs quickly into the skin, making it perfect for daily use without leaving any sticky residue. It helps improve overall skin texture, leaving your face feeling smooth, refreshed, and visibly revitalized.</p><p>Designed for convenience, the <strong>30g compact size</strong> is ideal for both home and travel use, allowing you to maintain your skincare routine wherever you go. Suitable for all skin types, this cream is a reliable choice for anyone looking to enhance their natural beauty and achieve a radiant complexion.</p>', 2000, 1790, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 15:35:51', '[]'),
(118, 'Jasnic Cebellox Anti-Hair Fall Spray 50ml', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Hair Color & Treatments', '<h3><strong>Ō£© Key Features</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Anti-Hair Fall Formula</strong> ŌĆō Helps reduce hair breakage and supports stronger, healthier strands.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Hair Growth Support</strong> ŌĆō Nourishes hair roots and promotes natural hair growth.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight Spray</strong> ŌĆō Non-greasy formula that absorbs quickly without weighing hair down.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Scalp Nourishment</strong> ŌĆō Enriched with active ingredients to improve scalp health.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Strengthens Hair Roots</strong> ŌĆō Helps reinforce follicles to minimize hair fall over time.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy Spray Application</strong> ŌĆō Convenient spray design for quick and even usage.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Suitable for Daily Use</strong> ŌĆō Gentle enough for regular application on all hair types.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Improves Hair Texture</strong> ŌĆō Leaves hair looking smoother, shinier, and more manageable.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Compact 50ml Size</strong> ŌĆō Travel-friendly and easy to carry anywhere.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Refreshing &amp; Revitalizing</strong> ŌĆō Keeps scalp feeling fresh and energized.</li></ol>', '<p>Take control of hair fall and restore confidence with the <strong>Jasnic Cebellox Anti-Hair Fall Spray 50ml</strong>. Specially formulated to support healthier, stronger hair, this advanced spray targets weak roots and thinning hair, helping you achieve fuller and more resilient strands over time.</p><p>Infused with <strong>hair-nourishing and strengthening ingredients</strong>, this spray works directly on the scalp to improve hair texture and reduce breakage. It helps revitalize hair follicles, promoting healthier growth while minimizing hair fall caused by daily stress, pollution, and environmental factors.</p><p>The <strong>lightweight, non-greasy formula</strong> absorbs quickly into the scalp without leaving residue, making it perfect for daily use. Its easy-to-use spray application ensures even distribution, allowing the active ingredients to reach deep into the roots for maximum effectiveness.</p><p>Designed for both men and women, the <strong>50ml compact size</strong> is convenient for home use and travel, so you can maintain your hair care routine anytime, anywhere. With consistent use, your hair feels stronger, looks healthier, and appears visibly fuller.</p>', 7000, 4600, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 15:42:24', '[]'),
(119, 'Nourishing Hair Oil for Growth & Strength', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Hair Color & Treatments', '<h3><strong>Key Features ŌĆō</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Promotes Hair Growth</strong> ŌĆō Enriched with essential nutrients that support natural hair growth.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Strengthens Hair Roots</strong> ŌĆō Helps reduce hair fall by nourishing and reinforcing follicles.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Deep Nourishment</strong> ŌĆō Penetrates deeply to hydrate scalp and hair from root to tip.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Improves Hair Texture</strong> ŌĆō Leaves hair softer, smoother, and more manageable.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Adds Natural Shine</strong> ŌĆō Enhances hairŌĆÖs natural glow and healthy appearance.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Scalp Care Formula</strong> ŌĆō Helps maintain a healthy scalp and reduces dryness.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight &amp; Non-Sticky</strong> ŌĆō Easy-to-apply oil that doesnŌĆÖt feel heavy or greasy.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Suitable for All Hair Types</strong> ŌĆō Ideal for men and women with all hair textures.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Reduces Frizz &amp; Breakage</strong> ŌĆō Helps control frizz and minimizes split ends.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Daily or Weekly Use</strong> ŌĆō Perfect for regular hair care routines or deep oil treatments.</li></ol>', '<p>Transform your hair care routine with the <strong>Nourishing Hair Oil for Growth &amp; Strength</strong>, a powerful blend designed to promote healthy hair growth while strengthening your roots. Perfect for all hair types, this oil deeply nourishes the scalp and revitalizes dull, weak hair from root to tip.</p><p>Infused with <strong>natural oils and essential nutrients</strong>, this formula penetrates deep into the scalp to improve blood circulation and support stronger hair growth. It helps reduce hair fall, repair damage, and restore shine, leaving your hair softer, smoother, and more manageable.</p><p>The <strong>lightweight, non-greasy texture</strong> ensures easy absorption without weighing your hair down, making it suitable for regular use. Whether used as a pre-wash treatment or overnight nourishment, it works effectively to improve hair texture and overall health.</p><p>With consistent use, the Nourishing Hair Oil helps bring back your hairŌĆÖs natural strength, thickness, and shineŌĆögiving you visibly healthier and fuller-looking hair.</p>', 780, 690, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 15:46:41', '[]'),
(121, '  Minoxidil 5% + Finasteride 0.25% Topical Solution', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Hair Color & Treatments', '<h3><strong>Ō£© Key Features ŌĆō</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Dual-Action Formula</strong> ŌĆō Combines Minoxidil and Finasteride for a comprehensive approach to hair loss treatment.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Promotes Hair Regrowth</strong> ŌĆō Helps stimulate hair follicles and encourage new hair growth.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Reduces Hair Thinning</strong> ŌĆō Works to slow down hair loss and improve hair density.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Targets Root Cause</strong> ŌĆō Finasteride helps block DHT, a key factor in hair loss.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Improves Scalp Circulation</strong> ŌĆō Minoxidil enhances blood flow to nourish hair follicles.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Topical Application</strong> ŌĆō Easy-to-apply solution directly on affected areas.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Clinically Supported Ingredients</strong> ŌĆō Backed by widely used and researched hair treatment components.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Non-Greasy Formula</strong> ŌĆō Lightweight and fast-absorbing for convenient daily use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Suitable for Regular Use</strong> ŌĆō Designed for consistent application as part of a hair care routine.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Noticeable Results Over Time</strong> ŌĆō Helps improve hair thickness and coverage with continued use.</li></ol>', '<p>Take a targeted approach to hair restoration with the <strong>Minoxidil 5% + Finasteride 0.25% Topical Solution</strong>, a clinically backed formula designed to help reduce hair loss and support regrowth. This dual-action treatment combines two powerful ingredients to address hair thinning at the root level and promote healthier, fuller-looking hair.</p><p>The formula features <strong>Minoxidil 5%</strong>, which helps improve blood flow to hair follicles, stimulating growth and extending the hair growth cycle. It is paired with <strong>Finasteride 0.25%</strong>, known for its ability to reduce DHT levels on the scalpŌĆöa key factor responsible for hair thinning and pattern hair loss.</p><p>Designed for <strong>topical application</strong>, this solution works directly on the scalp, targeting affected areas without the need for oral medication. The lightweight, fast-absorbing formula ensures easy daily use without leaving a greasy residue, making it suitable for regular application as part of your hair care routine.</p><p>With consistent use, this treatment helps <strong>reduce hair fall, strengthen existing hair, and promote visible regrowth</strong>, resulting in thicker, healthier-looking hair over time. Ideal for individuals experiencing early to moderate hair thinning, it offers a convenient and effective solution backed by proven ingredients.</p>', 1780, 1490, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 15:50:47', '[]'),
(122, 'ProScalp Volumizing Shampoo - Boost Hair Volume and Health', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Hair Color & Treatments', '<h3><strong>Key Features</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Boosts Hair Volume</strong> ŌĆō Adds natural fullness and body to fine or limp hair.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Nourishing Formula</strong> ŌĆō Enriched with vitamins and botanical extracts to strengthen hair from root to tip.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Gentle Cleansing</strong> ŌĆō Removes dirt, oil, and buildup without stripping natural moisture.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Improves Hair Health</strong> ŌĆō Promotes stronger, healthier, and more resilient strands.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Lightweight &amp; Non-Greasy</strong> ŌĆō Leaves hair soft, smooth, and bouncy without weighing it down.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Scalp Care</strong> ŌĆō Supports a clean, balanced scalp for better hair growth.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Suitable for Daily Use</strong> ŌĆō Mild formula safe for everyday application on all hair types.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Shine &amp; Smoothness</strong> ŌĆō Enhances hair texture and natural shine.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Refreshing Fragrance</strong> ŌĆō Leaves hair smelling fresh and revitalized.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Professional Quality</strong> ŌĆō Salon-grade formula designed for optimum results at home.</li></ol>', '<p>Give your hair the lift it deserves with <strong>ProScalp Volumizing Shampoo</strong>, specially formulated to add body, bounce, and vitality to fine or limp hair. Designed for daily use, this shampoo cleanses gently while promoting thicker, healthier-looking hair from root to tip.</p><p>Infused with <strong>nourishing botanical extracts and strengthening ingredients</strong>, ProScalp Shampoo revitalizes the scalp, improves hair texture, and enhances natural volume. It helps reduce breakage, leaving your hair feeling soft, smooth, and more manageable.</p><p>The <strong>lightweight, sulfate-free formula</strong> ensures gentle cleansing without stripping natural oils, making it suitable for all hair types, including color-treated hair. With regular use, it provides a noticeable boost in hair fullness, shine, and overall health.</p><p>Whether youŌĆÖre preparing for a special occasion or seeking a daily hair care solution, <strong>ProScalp Volumizing Shampoo</strong> delivers thicker, stronger, and more vibrant hair, helping you look and feel your best every day.</p>', 1080, 990, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 15:58:08', '[]'),
(123, '  Derma Roller System ŌĆō Skin Regeneration & Collagen Boosting Therapy', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Hair Color & Treatments', '<h3><strong>Key Features</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Advanced Skin Regeneration</strong> ŌĆō Stimulates natural healing and renewal for healthier-looking skin.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Collagen &amp; Elastin Boost</strong> ŌĆō Promotes collagen production to improve skin elasticity and firmness.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Microneedling Therapy</strong> ŌĆō Precision micro-needles enhance absorption of skincare products.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Improves Skin Texture</strong> ŌĆō Reduces appearance of fine lines, wrinkles, and uneven skin tone.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Reduces Scars &amp; Pigmentation</strong> ŌĆō Helps diminish acne scars, stretch marks, and dark spots over time.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Safe &amp; Hygienic Design</strong> ŌĆō High-quality, medical-grade needles for effective and safe use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy to Use at Home</strong> ŌĆō Ergonomic handle and roller system for comfortable application.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Boosts Product Effectiveness</strong> ŌĆō Maximizes absorption of serums, creams, and oils.</li></ol>', '<p>Experience professional-level skincare at home with the <strong>Derma Roller System</strong>, designed to stimulate skin regeneration, boost collagen production, and enhance the overall texture and appearance of your skin. Ideal for reducing fine lines, wrinkles, acne scars, and uneven skin tone, this system helps you achieve smoother, healthier, and more youthful-looking skin.</p><p>The roller features <strong>ultra-fine, precision-engineered micro-needles</strong> that gently penetrate the skinŌĆÖs surface to promote natural collagen and elastin production. This process helps improve skin firmness, elasticity, and texture while enhancing the absorption of serums and skincare treatments for maximum effectiveness.</p><p>Crafted for safety and durability, the <strong>Derma Roller System</strong> is easy to use at home or as part of a professional skincare routine. Its ergonomic handle and lightweight design ensure precise control, while the sterilizable roller head allows for hygienic and repeated use.</p><p>With consistent use, this system supports <strong>skin rejuvenation, reduction of fine lines and scars, and a radiant, refreshed complexion</strong>. It is suitable for all skin types and a versatile addition to any anti-aging or skincare regimen.</p>', 806, 700, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 16:02:34', '[]'),
(124, 'ELCEA BLACK HAIR DYE - PERMANENT HAIR DYE 1', 'Beauty & Wellness', 'Hair Color & Treatments', '<h3><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Natural Ingredients for Striking Black Hair:</strong></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Elcea Black Permanent Hair Dye ŌĆō 1 takes a unique approach to achieving a deep and bold hair color. Here\'s a breakdown of its potential benefits:</span></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Natural-Origin Formula (89%):</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> This dye is formulated with a high percentage of natural-origin ingredients, offering a potentially gentler alternative to harsh chemical dyes often used for vibrant colors.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Hibiscus Milk:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> This ingredient is included for its potential hair-stimulating properties.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Ammonia-Free:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> The absence of ammonia might contribute to a more pleasant fragrance during the coloring process and potentially minimize scalp irritation.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Black Hue:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> This shade aims to achieve a stunning, intense black color, adding a dramatic statement to your look.</span></li></ol>', '<h3><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Complete Gray Coverage and Long-Lasting Results:</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Despite containing natural ingredients, Elcea Black Permanent Hair Dye ŌĆō 1 strives to deliver on color vibrancy and longevity:</span></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">100% Gray Coverage:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> This dye claims to effectively cover all your gray hairs in just one application.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Long-Lasting Hold and Shine:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> The formula might provide long-lasting color vibrancy and shine, ensuring your black hair looks polished and radiant.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Gentle on the Scalp:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> The dye is designed to be gentle on your scalp, potentially minimizing irritation associated with some hair coloring products.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Professional Results:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> Elcea Black Permanent Hair Dye ŌĆō 1 aims to deliver salon-quality color results you can achieve at home.</span></li></ol><h3><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Nourishing Aftercare with Hibiscus Milk (Revitalizing Treatment):</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Elcea includes a revitalizing treatment with the dye kit. Here\'s what this additional step might offer:</span></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Enhanced Color Vibrancy:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> The treatment might help boost the vibrancy and shine of your black hair color.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Nourishing Hibiscus Milk:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> This ingredient could potentially nourish and soften your hair after coloring, minimizing dryness often associated with bold hair colors.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">UV Protection:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> The treatment might include a UV filter to help protect your colored hair from sun damage, which can cause fading.</span></li></ol><h3><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Important Note:</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">While the claims sound promising, it\'s important to remember that individual results may vary. It\'s always recommended to perform a strand test before full application, especially if you have </span><u style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(12, 169, 106);\">sensitive skin</u><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\"> or scalp. Additionally, consult a hairstylist for professional advice on color selection and application, especially if you have dark hair or have never colored your hair before. Bleaching may be required to achieve the desired black shade on lighter hair.</span></p><h3><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Natural-Looking Option for Bold Black Hair:</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(42, 42, 42);\">Elcea Black Hair Dye ŌĆō 1: Bold black shade, 100% gray coverage, gentle formula. Strand test advised; consult professional. Pre-bleaching for lighter hair</span></p>', 6500, 5000, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 16:09:08', '[]');
