(125, 'S9 Max 2.19 Inch Display Series 9 Smartwatch', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Smart Watch & Smart TV', '<h3><strong>Ō£© Key Features ŌĆō S9 Max Series 9 Smartwatch</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Large 2.19-Inch HD Display</strong> ŌĆō Wide, vibrant screen for easy navigation and clear visuals.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Multiple Sports Modes</strong> ŌĆō Supports tracking for running, cycling, walking, and more.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Smart Notifications</strong> ŌĆō Receive calls, messages, and app alerts directly on your wrist.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Long-Lasting Battery</strong> ŌĆō Extended battery life for uninterrupted daily use.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Stylish &amp; Modern Design</strong> ŌĆō Sleek look suitable for casual, sports, and formal wear.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Water-Resistant</strong> ŌĆō Safe for daily wear, workouts, and light water exposure.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Customizable Watch Faces</strong> ŌĆō Personalize your display with multiple themes and styles.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Easy Compatibility</strong> ŌĆō Works seamlessly with Android and iOS smartphones.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong>Touchscreen &amp; User-Friendly Interface</strong> ŌĆō Intuitive control for smooth operation.</li></ol>', '<p>Stay connected, track your fitness, and elevate your style with the <strong>S9 Max 2.19 Inch Display Series 9 Smartwatch</strong>. Designed for modern lifestyles, this smartwatch combines cutting-edge technology with a sleek, contemporary design to keep you informed, active, and in controlŌĆöall from your wrist.</p><p>Featuring a <strong>large 2.19-inch full-color display</strong>, the S9 Max provides clear, vibrant visuals for notifications, calls, messages, and fitness tracking. Its intuitive touchscreen interface makes navigation smooth and effortless, putting all your essential features just a tap away.</p><p>The smartwatch comes equipped with <strong>comprehensive health and fitness tracking</strong>, including heart rate monitoring, blood oxygen (SpOŌéé) measurement, step counting, calorie tracking, sleep monitoring, and more. Stay on top of your wellness goals while monitoring your daily activity and progress.</p><p>With <strong>smart connectivity features</strong>, the S9 Max allows you to receive notifications, control music, track your calendar, and even answer calls directly from your wrist. Its durable build and stylish design make it suitable for both casual and formal settings, while the long-lasting battery ensures uninterrupted usage throughout the day.</p>', 1500, 1200, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 16:23:47', '[]'),
(126, 'Joyroom JR-FT5 Pro Fit-Life Smartwatch with Call Feature', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Smart Watch & Smart TV', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Joyroom JR-FT5 Pro Fit-Life Series Smartwatch Features:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">1.83ŌĆ│ large HD TFT screen</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Single-chip, dual mode; one button to make/ answer calls, easy to operate</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">80+ sports modes, intelligent selection, and more professional exercise</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Rotate the button to switch the dial page</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Online and custom dial styles of your choice; create your style</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">IP68 water resistance, worry-free usage</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Accurately master health data; auto-monitoring of heart rate, blood pressure, blood oxygen, stress, and sleep</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Real-time sync with incoming calls and APP messages reminds you in a timely and presents you clearly</span></li></ol>', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Joyroom JR-FT5 Pro Fit-Life Series Smartwatch in Rose Gold combines style and functionality. This smartwatch features a 1.83ŌĆ│ HD TFT screen, supports 80+ sports modes, real-time health monitoring, and IP68 water resistance. With Bluetooth connectivity, you can answer and make calls seamlessly. Customize your dial, track your fitness, and stay connected, designed for a dynamic lifestyle.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Joyroom Fit-Life Series Smartwatch Specifications:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Brand: Joyroom</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Name: Fit-Life Series Smart Watch (Answer/Make Call)</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Model: JR-FT5</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Screen material: TFT</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Screen size: 1.83ŌĆØ</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">BT version: BLE5.3+BT3.0</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">BT chip: JL7012/F6</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Memory: 64MB</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Waterproof rating: IP68</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">BT range: about 10m</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Screen resolution: 240*286</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Touch control mode: capacitive touch control</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Battery capacity: 300mAh</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Charging time: about 2.5h</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Standby time (connected): about 15 days</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Typical usage time: about 7-10 days</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Charging mode: magnetic charging</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Charging input: 5VŌÄō500mA</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Overall size: 36.5*44.7*11.5</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Band material: silicone</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Band size: 219*20</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Applicable wrist size: 50-220</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Body material: top shell: zinc alloy; base shell: PC+ABS</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Weight: about 50g</span></li></ol>', 10000, 8750, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 16:48:36', '[]'),
(127, 'X8 Plus Ultra Smartwatch Series 8 NFC 2.08 Inch Display & Wireless Charging', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Smart Watch & Smart TV', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">X8 Plus Technical Specifications:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bluetooth-compatible Version:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> 5.0</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Wi-Fi:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> No</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Metrics Measured:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Heart Rate Monitor, Blood Oxygen Monitor, Sleep Monitor</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Activity Tracked:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Steps Tracker, Distance Tracker, Calorie Tracker, Activity Tracker</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Touch Screen:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> YES</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Band Detachable:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Yes</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Battery Detachable:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> No</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">CPU Model:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> HS6621-PG</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">CPU Manufacturer:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> MediaTek</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">RAM:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> &lt;128MB</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">ROM:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> &lt;128MB</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">System:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> None</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Type:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> On Wrist</span></li></ol><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">X8 Plus Power and Battery:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Battery Capacity:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 117, 117); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> 220- 300mAh</span></li></ol>', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">The X8 Plus Ultra Smartwatch Series 8 NFC features a 2.08-inch always-on display, wireless charging, and comes in an attractive 49mm orange and black design. ItŌĆÖs a versatile sports watch suitable for adults and compatible with multiple languages. With various health metrics like heart rate and blood oxygen monitoring, it tracks steps, distance, and calories. It connects via Bluetooth 5.0 and has a 220- 300mAh battery. The watchŌĆÖs functionality includes call and message reminders, remote control, and more, all managed through the WearFit Pro app. Stay connected and active with this stylish smartwatch.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Blood Oxygen Monitoring: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">When blood oxygen levels are low, it is easy to cause Fatigue and sleepiness to dropŌĆöintelligent monitoring of blood oxygen saturation and degrees, looking after your around-the-clock blood oxygen health.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Heart Rate Monitoring: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Monitor your heart rate in real-time; find out when you feel unwell in time, have abnormal heart rate beats, and are more concerned. Your heart is healthy.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Sleep Monitoring: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Monitor your different sleep stages, including profound sleep/light sleep/nocturnal wakefulness. Scientific assessment of sleep quality effectively improves sleep.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Breathing Training: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">You can relax in time with breathing exercises, fit, recover, and relax. Helps in yoga practice.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Message Push: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">New push interaction form: top pop-up window. Click the ŌĆśpop-up boxŌĆÖ to enter the message details. After the message pops up, swipe the screen/click the button to hide the message.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">What to Practice, Multi-sport Mode as You Choose: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">No matter what sport you enjoy, there is a fitness training program for you. Choose running, basketball, football, cycling, or any other sport you are interested in. Exercise to your heartŌĆÖs content will help you track your every move.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Artificial Intelligence Voice Assistant: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Exclusive AI voice algorithm, the voice assistant is on call. Completely free your hands and complete some voice operations.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Fishing artifact: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Remote control mobile phone vibrato, read novels, switch videos, and like.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Bluetooth Calling: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Swipe to answer incoming calls, dial calls, sync phone call records with high-definition sound quality, Free call back, and free answer.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Two-Way Payment: My QR code Business Card:  </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Alipay payment/receipt, WeChat payment, QR code business card. Whether you buy a drink during exercise, come back from a workout to purchase dinner, add friends, etc., you need to use a mobile phone or lift your wrist to scan. You can scan the code in seconds with your watch, which is convenient and fast.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Uninterrupted Bluetooth Music: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">When you go out for a run, bring your smartwatch and listen to it while you run. After returning home, turn on the phone, the music is uninterrupted, and the good songs continue to be listened to.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Multifunctional NFC Get it Done in One Table: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">New online function, support company/community access card simulation. It is more convenient to lift the wrist to open.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">The Big Screen Feels Different: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">The larger display screen dramatically improves the overall user experience. All kinds of content are more apparent at a glance, and all sorts of operations are more comfortable. a new generation of 2.08-inch high-definition full screen, High-pixel display resolution, narrow frame design of the body, rejecting the interruption of heavy black borders, bringing you a more comprehensive visual enjoyment.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">New Dial Design / A Lot / Fun / Nice: </strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">This </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(69, 180, 77);\">X8 Plus Ultra Smartwatch</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> has built-in new dials, including various dynamic dials. In addition, there are 200+ personalized dials on the dial market for you to choose from.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Custom Component: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Customize the function of shortcut components and adjust standard features according to your needs.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Bedside Lamp Mode Gravity sensor: </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">The horizontal screen and the vertical screen are automatically switched, and the charging always-on mode is not dazzling. Say goodbye to the bedside blindness at night.</span></p><h3 class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(37, 37, 37);\">X8 Plus Ultra Smartwatch Specifications:</span></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Brand Name:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> EranTech</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Category:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Smart Watches</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Style:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> SPORT</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Application Age Group:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Adult</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Compatibility:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> All Compatible</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet