17, 117);\">SIM Card Available:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> No</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Mechanism:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> No</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Multiple Dials:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Yes</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">GPS:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> No</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Network Mode:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> None</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Screen Size:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> 2.08 INCH</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Resolution:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> 390*435</span></li></ol><p class=