(128, 'Skyworth 75Q6600G-QLED 4K Smart Google TV', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Smart Watch & Smart TV', '<h2><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 62, 72);\">Features:</strong></h2><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 62, 72);\">Eye Care</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 62, 72);\">Game Mode: YES</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 62, 72);\">Contrast Ratio: 1400:1</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 62, 72);\">Refresh Rate: 60Hz</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 62, 72);\">4K QLED Google TV OS</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 62, 72);\">Google Assistant  Voice Control</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 62, 72);\">Netflix//Disney+/DSTV/SHOWMAX </span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 62, 72);\">YouTube/YouTube HDR/Prime Video: YES</span></li></ol>', '<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(125, 125, 125);\">The </span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(125, 125, 125);\">Skyworth 75Q6600G-QLED 4K Smart Google TV</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(125, 125, 125);\"> features a 75-inch QLED display with 4K resolution (3840 x 2160 pixels), delivering stunningly detailed and vibrant visuals. It runs on Google TV, offering access to a wide range of streaming apps and services. With built-in Chromecast, you can easily stream content from your smartphone or computer. It also includes Google Assistant for voice control and supports Dolby Vision and Dolby Atmos for enhanced picture and audio quality. This TV is perfect for larger living rooms or home theaters.</span></p>', 300000, 269900, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 16:57:41', '[]'),
(129, 'Xiaomi Mi Smart Band 4 Fitness Tracker', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Smart Watch & Smart TV', '<p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Specification</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Special Features: Health tracker: Measurement of heart rate, Sleep management, Pedometer, Calories burned measuring, Steps counting, Distance recording, Sedentary reminder.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Other functions: Stopwatch, Alarm clock, Timer, Find my phone, Phone unlock, Event reminder, Do not disturb mode (works even without phone), Lock screen, Music controls on band</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Alert type: Vibration</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Sensors: 3-axis accelerometer, 3-axis gyroscope, Capacitive proximity sensor, optical heart rate sensor</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Screen: 0.95-inch Color AMOLED Display</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Resolution: 120*240RGB</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Touch key: Yes</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Battery type: Lithium polymer battery</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Battery capacity:135mAh</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Standby time: About 20 days</span></li></ol>', '<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">120 x 240 pixels, Screen brightness up to 450 nits, all-new user interface ŌĆō smoother and simplified touch screen experience, brightness adjustment mode, 2.5D tempered glass with anti-fingerprint coating. One of the things that set the Mi Band 4 apart from many other feature-laden smartwatches available is its 5ATM water-resistant rating ŌĆō withstands pressures equivalent to a depth of 50 meters, making it a charm when being exposed in rain, splashing, accidental submersion, showering, surface, swimming. In the sports modes of the MIFIT APP, if you turn on one of the sports modes of the treadmill, outdoor running, riding, or fast walking, just lift your wrist and check the length, mileage, heart rate, speed, and other data on your bracelet. While Bluetooth connecting, if there is an incoming call, it would show the caller ID. Almost notification of APPs could be synchronized to the watch. Support to check the latest 5 messages, If each text of the message exceeds the display, touch the button can display on the next page. (up to 3 pages can be displayed). Raise your hand to brighten the screen without taping screen to see real-time states including sports data, time, and heart rate. Mi Band 4 helps you record all your activities in the day, calculate the distance you walk and calories burned, take care of your health, monitor your sleep, remind you to have a rest, and track your steps, mileage and calories for high-quality sports. It tracks your heart rate continuously at every moment every day. Heart rate recording will start automatically once you wear it on. Xiaomi mi band 4 with ensures about 20 days ultra-long standby time for a full charging.</span></p>', 6500, 5650, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 17:02:11', '[]');
