(131, 'Xtrike-Me HD-215 Bluetooth 5.3V Wireless Headset', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Audio & Accessories', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Xtrike-Me HD-215 Bluetooth 5.3 Wireless Headset Key Features:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Crystal-Clear Stereo Sound ŌĆō</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Enjoy rich bass, detailed mids, and crisp highs for music, calls, and gaming.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Noise Isolation Technology ŌĆō</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Reduces background noise for clearer communication and immersive audio.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Bluetooth 5.3 Wireless ŌĆō</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Faster pairing, stable connection, and wider range.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Comfortable &amp; Ergonomic Design ŌĆō</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Lightweight build with soft, rotatable ear cups for long-hour wear.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Built-in Volume &amp; Playback Controls ŌĆō</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Manage calls, tracks, and volume directly from the headset.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Foldable &amp; Portable ŌĆō</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Easy to carry anywhere, perfect for travel and daily use.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Long Battery Life ŌĆō</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Extended playtime without frequent recharging.</span></li></ol>', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Experience premium audio freedom with the Xtrike-Me HD-215 Bluetooth Wireless Headset. Designed for gamers, music lovers, and professionals, this headset combines advanced sound technology with Bluetooth 5.3 connectivity for seamless, stable, and low-latency performance.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Why Choose the Xtrike-Me HD-215?</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Whether youŌĆÖre streaming, gaming, working, or listening to music, the Xtrike-Me HD-215 delivers performance, comfort, and convenience in one sleek design. Its modern black finish, foldable structure, and user-friendly controls make it a reliable choice for everyday use.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"backgrou