, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Experience the future of wireless audio with </span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">AirPods Pro 3 Master Copy</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> ŌĆö PakistanŌĆÖs most advanced premium master copy, delivering authentic Apple-style features at an unbeatable price. Designed to match the iconic look, feel, and functionality of the original AirPods, this model also includes practical enhancements that make it ideal for everyday use.</span></p><h3 class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(37, 37, 37);\">Apple AirPods Pro 3 ANC (3rd Generation) Master Copy</strong></h3><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">The Apple AirPods Pro 3 Master Copy is an upgraded version of the popular </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(69, 180, 77);\">Apple AirPods Pro 2 Master Copy</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">, offering noticeable improvements in design, features, and overall performance. Unlike basic TWS earbuds or older knockoffs, the Pro 3 supports a 2nd-generation, original-style connectivity pop-up, enabling instant pairing just like real AirPods. Finished in a sleek, Apple-inspired design, it delivers enhanced sound quality with up to 5ŌĆō6 hours of playback, making it one of the best-value premium AirPods master copies available in Pakistan.</span></p>', 6500, 4999, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 17:24:25', '[]'),
(133, 'MINI8 RTS Lavalier Metal Condenser Lightweight Wireless Dual Microphone', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Audio & Accessories', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">MINI8 RTS Lightweight Wireless Dual Microphone Key Features:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Wireless condenser microphone with Type-C connector</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Lightweight and portable ŌĆō perfect for mobile use</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Noise-cancelling technology for clear audio in noisy environments</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Wide 20HzŌĆō20KHz frequency response for natural sound</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Durable ABS, metal, and plastic construction</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Omni-directional pickup for consistent voice capture</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Stylish design with RGB LED lighting</span></li></ol>', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">The RTS Mini8 Wireless Microphone is a compact and professional condenser mic designed for mobile phones, cameras, and teaching applications. With its light-weight, portable design and noise-cancelling technology, it delivers clear, high-quality sound for vlogging, live streaming, online classes, and content creation.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Built with durable ABS, metal, and plastic materials, this wireless microphone is engineered for long-lasting performance. Its omnidirectional polar pattern ensures accurate sound pickup from all directions, while the 20HzŌĆō20KHz frequency response captures every detail of voice and music with clarity.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">The RTS Mini8 Microphone supports Type-C connectivity, offering plug-and-play convenience without extra accessories. Featuring RGB LED lights and a sleek private mold design, it combines modern style with professional functionality.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Whether youŌĆÖre a teacher, vlogger, or content creator, the Rts Mini8 provides reliable audio performance with a 65dB signal-to-noise ratio and 110dB maximum SPLŌĆöperfect for recording, streaming, and presentations in any environment.</span></p>', 6900, 4850, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 17:26:51', '[]'),
(134, 'LP18 UFO Wireless Bluetooth Home Theater Speaker', 'Electronics & Gadgets', 'Audio & Accessories', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Functionality:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Features:</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify ql-indent-1\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Dual speaker bass diaphragm</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify ql-indent-1\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Heavy bass stereo</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify ql-indent-1\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">RGB lighting effect</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify ql-indent-1\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">HIFI sound effect</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Connection Options:</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify ql-indent-1\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">TF card</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify ql-indent-1\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">3.5 MM audio jack</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify ql-indent-1\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Bluetooth connection</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Power Supply:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Built-in lithium battery</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Playing Time:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> 6 hours</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Speaker Adjustment Method:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\"> Touch</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Additional Information:</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-indent-1 ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Applicable Scenarios: Home</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-indent-1 ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">APP Supported: No</span></li></ol>', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">LP18 UFO Audio Space Wireless Bluetooth Speaker delivers powerful 80W sound with deep bass and immersive stereo performance. Featuring RGB lighting, touch controls, and Bluetooth 5.4 connectivity, this black &amp; gold home theater speaker is designed for bold style and rich audio. Enjoy up to 6 hours of playtime with support for TF card, 3.5mm jack, and MP3 playbackŌĆöperfect for modern home entertainment setups.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">LP18 UFO Audio Space Wireless Bluetooth Speaker General Information:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Model: </span><a href=\"https://pakistanstore.pk/product/wireless-bluetooth-home-theater-speaker/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(69, 180, 77);\">LP18 Speaker</a></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Target Group: Teenagers and above</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Smart Type: Other intelligence</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Appearance:</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Size: 310 x 120 x 350 mm</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Weight: 2100 g</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Shell Material: Metal</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Speaker Material: ABS plastic, Neodymium magnets</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Colors Available: Black &amp; Gold</span></li></ol><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">LP18 Home Theater Speaker Specifications:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Speaker Unit: Three speakers</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Speaker Size: 10 cm</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Rated Power: 80 W</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Bluetooth Version: 5.4</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Receiving Distance: 10m and above</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Channel: Other</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Expandable Storage: Not supported</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\" class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(117, 117, 117);\">Supported Formats: MP3</span></li></ol>', 16797, 14999, '[]', '[]', '2026-03-17 17:30:18', '[]');
